dvitīyo vibhāgaḥ |
namāmi vigrahaṃ sāmvaṃ saṃsāraviṣabheṣajam || 1 ||
svādhyāyādhyayane yuktāḥ svasthacittāḥ suniścalāḥ ||
sarvopadravanirmuktāḥ sarvaśatruvivarjitāḥ || 3 ||
abhyāgatānāmārtānāmatithīnāṃ priyaṃvadāḥ ||
maitryā karuṇayā yuktāḥ kumatāvapyupekṣakāḥ || 4 ||
parapuṣṭau mahāprītāḥ prajñāmānavivarjitāḥ ||
gavāṃ śuśrūṣaṇe yuktā guruśuśrūṣaṇe ratāḥ || 5 ||
ṛjavo mṛdavaḥ svasthāḥ sarvadvaṃdvavivarjitāḥ || 6 ||
rudrākṣamālābharaṇāḥ sitamasmāvaguṇṭhitāḥ ||
tripuṇḍāvalibhirdīptā jaṭāvalkalasaṃyutāḥ || 7 ||
śivābhimānasaṃpannāḥ śivabhaktiparāyaṇāḥ || 8 ||
saṃsāravipavṛkṣasya mūlacchedanatatparāḥ || 9 ||
vyāsaprasādasaṃpannaṃ viśvajñānamahodadhim || 10 ||
smṛtvā bhaktyā mahātmānaṃ tuṣṭuvuḥ sūtamuttamam ||11||
sarvajñaḥ sarvabhūtānāmabhīṣṭaphaladaḥ prabhuḥ || 12 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā munayaḥ sarve vismitā gadradasvarāḥ || 13 ||
pādaprakṣālanaṃ kṛtvā śraddhayā parayā saha || 14 ||
samāśvāsya ciraṃ kālaṃ prasannamukhapaṅkajam || 15 ||
sūtasaṃhitā 1
so'pi sūtaḥ svamācāryai smṛtvā śaṃbhuṃ jagadgurum || 16||
sarvavidyāmayīmīśāṃ sākṣādvighnavināyakam ||
ṣaṇmukhaṃ ca sadā śuddhaṃ praṇamya bhuvi daṇḍavat || 17 ||
kṛtāñjalipuṭo bhūtvā munīnālokya suvratān ||
vaktumārabhate sūtaḥ sarvavedārthamuttamam || 18 ||
namāmi saṃsāramahāviṣauṣadham || 19 ||
parānubhūtiṃ bhavapāśanāśanīṃ
namāmi nānāvidhalokavaibhavām || 20 ||
atha vakṣyāmi vedārthe śṛṇuta śraddhayā dvijāḥ ||
śraddhayā rahitaṃ sarve phalāya na kadācana || 1 ||
munipraśnānantaryamathaśabdārthaḥ || 1 ||
adhiṣṭhānāvaśeṣo hi nāśaḥ kalpitavastunaḥ ||
bhāvābhāvasvabhāvābhyāmanya eva hi kelpitaḥ || 8 ||
īśānaviṣayaṃ jñānaṃ vedāntaśravaṇādinā ||
jāyate parahaṃsasya yatermukhyādhikāriṇaḥ || 10 ||
nā''śramāntaraniṣṭhasya kramāttasyāpi jāyate || 11 ||
iti sākṣātpāraṃparyābhyām || 12 ||
kuṭīcakāśramadharmānuṣṭhānaphalam || 13 ||
dvitīyaḥ śāntidāntyādijñānānecchāmavāpnuyāt ||
tṛtīyo'khilavedāntaśravaṇecchāmavāmuyāt || 14 ||
parokṣaṃ brahmavijñānaṃ śābdaṃ deśikapūrvakam ||
buddhipūrvakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ kṛtsnaṃ dahati vahnivat || 16 ||
saṃsāranāśakaṃ proktaṃ tamasaścaṇḍabhānuvat || 17 ||
ato vijñānalābhāya parahaṃso bhaveddijaḥ || 18 ||
kuṭīcakāśca haṃsāśva tathā'nye ca bahūkāḥ ||
ye bhaviṣyanti te kuryuḥ prājāpatyeṣṭisaṃjñitām || 19 ||
āgneyeṣṭiṃ dvijāḥ kuryuḥ parahaṃsābhilāṣiṇaḥ ||
paścātraidhātavīṃ kuryuḥ sarve saṃyatamānasāḥ || 20 ||
ye'nāhitāgnayo viprāsteṣāṃ neṣṭirvidhīyate ||
virajākhyairmahāmantrairājyena caruṇā'pi ca || 21 ||
hutaśeṣaṃ caruṃ sājyaṃ prāśyā''camyaiva sarpiṣā ||
pūrṇāhutiṃ punaḥ kuryuḥ praṇavenāgnijāyayā || 22 ||
iti mantreṇa kuryuste maipoccāraṇamādarāt || 23 ||
saṃnyāsādhvaryuṇā dattaṃ daṇḍaṃ kāpāyameva ca || 24 ||
vedāntaśravaṇaṃ kuryurjñānārthaṃ bhikṣukottamāḥ || 25 ||
oṅkāraḥ sarvamantrāṇāmuttamaḥ parikīrtitaḥ ||
oṅkāreṇa lavenaiva saṃsārābdhi tariṣyati || 28 ||
kathaṃcitpraṇavasyārthā bhaviṣyanti na mukhyataḥ || 30 ||
sthānaṃ saṃsevanīyaṃ syāñcintanīyaṃ tathaiva ca || 31 ||
avimukte mahādevaḥ sākṣādiśveśvaraḥ prabhuḥ ||
upāsyamānaḥ suprīto jñānaṃ sākṣātprayacchati || 32 ||
naraḥ kiṃcidipaṃ bhuktvā kṣunivṛttiṃ kariṣyati || 33||
epā pañcākṣarī vidyā śatarudriyamadhyagā ||
pañcākṣare mahādevaḥ sarvadā supratiṣṭhitaḥ || 38 ||
mahādevasya sāṃnidhyādvyaṣṭibhūtāśva devatāḥ ||
tatra pratiṣṭhitā eva vṛkṣe śākhā yathā sthitāḥ || 39 ||
śive rudrajapātprīte prītā evānyadevatāḥ ||
ato rudrajapādeva bhuktimuktī prasidhyataḥ || 41 ||
māyā māheśvarī śaktiḥ sattvādiguṇabhedataḥ ||
jīvamākramya saṃsāre bhrāmayatyaniśaṃ dvijāḥ || 42 ||
sattvātsukhaṃ ca jñānaṃ ca vairāgyaṃ śauklyameva ca || 43 ||
moho bhrāntistathā''lasyaṃ kāryaṃ ca tamaso bhavet ||44||
sūtasaṃhitā !
'evamuttamarūpāśca padārthāḥ sattvasaṃbhavāḥ ||
tathā madhyamarūpāśca padārthā rājasāḥ smṛtāḥ ||
vihīnāstāmasā eva padārthāḥ saṃgraheṇa tu || 45 ||
ato māyāmayaḥ sākṣātsaṃsāraḥ sarvadehinām ||
sa śivajñānamātreṇa sadya eva nivartate || 46 ||
jñānayajñena viprāṇāmāstikānāmamāninām ||
jāyate paramaṃ jñānaṃ nānyathā munipuṅgavāḥ || 47 ||
jñānayajño bhavetsūkṣmaḥ sākṣātsaṃsāravādhakaḥ || 48 ||
kāyiko vācikaścaiva mānasaśceti suvratāḥ || 49 ||
mantrāṇāṃ japarūpastu vāciko vedavittamāḥ || 50 ||
kāyikādādhikaḥ prokto vāciko matimattaḥ || 51 ||
mānaso vācikācchreṣṭha mānaso bahudhā smṛtaḥ ||
dhyeyabhedena so'pyevamuttamācamabhedataḥ || 52 ||
viṣṇvādīnāṃ tu devānāṃ dhyānaṃ cādhamamipyate || 53 ||
ato mokṣārthibhiḥ prājñaiḥ śiva aikaḥ śivaṃkaraḥ ||
dhyeyaḥ sarva parityajya śivādanyaṃ tu daivatam || 54 ||
iti śrutiḥ śivajñānameva vadantī dhyānamantareṇa jñānāsaṃbhavāt jñānasya
rudraṃ viśvādhikaṃ viṣṇuṃ brahmāṇaṃ cānyameva vā ||
samaṃ saṃcintayansākṣātsaṃsāre parivartate || 57 ||
mahāpāpavatāṃ puṃsāṃ pūrvajanmasu suvratāḥ ||
viṣṇuḥ sarvādhiko bhāti na sākṣātparameśvaraḥ ||58||
viṣṇuḥ sarvādhiko bhāti nārakī sa na saṃśayaḥ ||
viṣṇuḥ sarvādhiko nāmya iti cintayatāṃ nṛṇām ||59||
tepāṃ naiva ca mokṣāśā kalpakoṭiśatairapi || 60 ||
adhomukhordhvapādāste yāsyanti narakārṇavam || 61 ||
sāmyaṃ vadanti ye teṣāṃ na saṃsārādvimokṣaṇam || 62 ||
viṣṇuprajāpatīndrādidevatāsu munīśvarāḥ ||
viṣṇvādidevatāḥ paśyankramānmucyeta bandhanāt || 64 ||
śivaṃ sarvottamaṃ viprā hariviṣṇvādināmataḥ ||
cintayanghorasaṃsāre patatyeva na saṃśayaḥ || 65 ||
yathā'mātyādibuddhistu rājñi bādhāya dehinām ||
tathā viṣṇvādibuddhistu śive vādhāya dehinām || 66 ||
ataḥ śivaḥ sadā dhyeyaḥ prādhānyena manīṣibhiḥ ||
jñānayajñātparo yajño nāsti nāsti śrutau smṛtau ||67||
mahāpāpavatāṃ nṛṇāṃ jñānayajño na rocate || 68 ||
viśuddhaṃ jñānamutpannaṃ yasya tasya mahātmanaḥ || 69 ||
rudramūrtiṣu sarvāsu śāntidāntyādisādhane || 70 ||
śivaliṅgasya prajāyāṃ śivasthāneṣu suvratāḥ || 71 ||
upekṣā vā na sa jñānī paśurvijñānavañcakaḥ || 72 ||
tathā'pyukteṣu sarveṣu śaiveṣu dvijapuṅgavāḥ ||
priyabuddhiḥ svato bhāti vādhitākārarūpataḥ || 74 ||
praśaṃsanti mahābhāgyājjñānayajñasya vaibhavam || 78 ||
aśaktā api vijñātuṃ jñānayajñasya vaibhavam ||
śraddhayā svādhikāreṇa vadanti jñānavaibhavam || 79 ||
vyāsaḥ sākṣācchivajñānī śivasyaiva prasādataḥ || 82 ||
tatprasādādahaṃ sākṣācchivajñānī na saṃśayaḥ ||
mayā tatsaṃgraheṇaiva proktaṃ yuṣmākamādarāt || 83 ||
jñātavantaḥ kṛtārthāśca yūyaṃ satyamidaṃ vacaḥ || 84 ||
itaḥ pūrva mayā'nyeṣāṃ nāyamartho'bhibhāṣitaḥ ||
vyāso mama guruḥ pūrva rahasyaṃ me'bhyabhāṣata || 85 ||
kastarhi jñānavānkathaṃ vā tadīyajñānasya kaṇādādivanna vijñānamātratā
sārātsārataraḥ sākṣādayamarthaḥ prabhāṣitaḥ ||
gopanīyastvayaṃ nityaṃ bhavadbhiḥ paramāstikaiḥ || 86 ||
1 . prakāśita: |
prādhānyena phalaṃ śuddhirārthikī kāmyakarmaṇaḥ || 2 ||
kevalaṃ pratyavāyasya nivṛttiritarasya tu || 3 ||
mahābhāgyāḥ pravartante teṣāṃ muktirayatnataḥ || 4 ||
aiṣu yajñeṣu sarveṣu teṣāṃ mandaphalaṃ bhavet || 5 ||
ऍṣu yajñeṣu te śīghraṃ vimuktiphalamāpnuyuḥ || 6 ||
iti vijñāya mānena svātmānaṃ tarkato'pi caṃ || 7 ||
yajñarūpaṃ mahāviṣṇuṃ yajñe paśyanti ye dvijāḥ ||
te tu vijñānamāsādya kaivalyaṃ jñānamāpnuyuḥ || 9 ||
iti jñātvā yajante ye te'pi vijñānamāpnuyuḥ ||10||
te yānti narakaṃ ghoraṃ yāvadābhūtasaṃplavam || 12 ||
11 33 11
sa eva sāmbaḥ sarvajña ijyaḥ sarvamahāmakhaiḥ || 13 ||
yāni karmāṇi sarvāṇi niṣiddhāni śrutau smṛtau ||
tāni cā''rādhanaṃ śaṃbhoriti jñānaṃ mahāmakhaḥ ||15||
īśvarārthadhiyā pāpānyapi karmāṇi suvratāḥ ||
bhavanti pūtānyatyantaṃ satyameva na saṃśayaḥ || 16 ||
ārdrakāṣṭhaṃ mahānagniḥ śuṣkaṃ kṛtvā dahedyathā ||
tatheśvaradhiyā pāpaṃ śuddhavijñānadaṃ bhavet || 17 ||
tanmahāpātakaṃ proktaṃ saṃsārasya pravartakam || 19 ||
vaidikaṃ tāntrikaṃ hitvā mārga svaprajñayā dvijāḥ ||
yatra yo devatāvṛddhi karoti śradvayā saha || 22 ||
athāhaṃ vācikaṃ yajñaṃ vakṣyāmi śraddhayā saha |
parātparatarāttasmācchivāccaitanyalakṣaṇāva || 1 ||
śabdaḥ sūkṣmaḥ svabhāvena prādurāsīdakhaṇḍitaḥ || 2 ||
sa śabdaḥ punarādhāre prāṇināmāstikottamāḥ ||
piṇḍībhūtatayā''bhāti taptajāmbūnadaprabhaḥ || 3 ||
ādhāre paraśaktestu sthāne śabdaḥ prakāśitaḥ || 6 ||
ājñāsaṃjñānmahāsthānādūrdhvaṃ yatsthānamuttamam || 7 ||
tatrastho'yaṃ dvijāḥ śabdaḥ sūkṣmekākṣaratāmiyāt ||
tṛtīye paramādhāre pūrake puṇyabhājane ||
ekākāratvamāproti svabhāvenākṣaradvayam || 8 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
mananatrāṇarūpatvānmantra ityabhiśabditaḥ || 9 ||
mātṛkā paramā devī mantramātā maheśvarī ||
asmādādyānmahāmantrādāvirbhūtā svabhāvataḥ || 10 ||
tasmācchrīmātṛkā śṛddhā cāṃ''dyamantrātmikī bhavet || 11||
vyastākṣarapā 6 ga ṭa evaṃ 7 gha. pāyāṃta |
mananatrāṇarūpatvānmantra ityabhiśabditaḥ || 9 ||
iva utpacyā mātṛkāpāstadutpattyā cānyeṣāṃ maitrāṇāṃ tadanusaṃdhānārthamasya
mātṛkā paramā devī mantramātā maheśvarī ||
asmādādyānmahāmantrādāvirbhūtā svabhāvataḥ || 10 ||
tasmācchrī mātṛkā śuddhā cā~''dyamantrātmikī bhavet || 11||
aparīkṣya pradānena śīghraṃ mṛtyumavāpnuyāt ||
jarjitaḥ puruṣārtho'pi vṛthā bhavati tasya tu || 16 ||
munibhiśva tathā devaiḥ sarvajñena śivena ca || 17 ||
mantrāṇāṃ mātṛbhūtā ca mātṛkā parameśvarī || 18 ||
sā punaḥ kramabhedena mahāmantrātmanā tathā || 19 ||
mantrātmanā ca vedādiśabdākāreṇa ca svataḥ ||
satyetareṇa śabdenāpyāvirbhavati suvratāḥ || 20 ||
yathā parataraḥ śaṃbhurvidhā śaktiśivātmanā ||
tathaiva mātṛkā devī dvidhābhūtā bhavetsvayam || 21 ||
ekākāreṇa śaktestu vācakaśvetareṇa tu ||
śivasya vācakaḥ sākṣādvidheyaṃ padagāminī || 22 ||
aṃśa ekaḥ padasyāyamupakārāya dehinām ||
bhavetpoḍaśacā pūrva pañcadhā ca dvidhā punaḥ || 25 ||
padasyāṃśo'paraḥ pūrvo dvātriṃśadamāpnuyāt ||
trayastriṃśatpunarbhedaṃ tathaiva dvividhaṃ bhavet || 26 ||
evaṃ lokopakārāya padaṃ bahuvidhaṃ bhavet || 27 ||
tāntrikāṃśca tathā''kārānupajīvanti kecana ||
laukikānapi cā''kārānupajīvanti kecana || 29 ||
yathā vā śaktimīśasya yathā vā bhūtapañcakam ||
tathā sarve padākārānupajīvanti sarvadā || 30 ||
mātṛkā paramā devī svapadākārameditā ||
vaikharīrūpatāmeti karaṇairviśadā svayam || 31 ||
sthūlā sūkṣmā susūkṣmā ca trividhā mātṛkeśvarī ||
sā devī śaktisaṃbhinnā śivasyāmitatejasaḥ || 32 ||
brahmaviṣṇvādidevānāmacintyaḥ sūkṣmatāvidhiḥ ||
cinmayaḥ paracidrūpaḥ śivāsaṃbhinna eva hi || 34 ||
ācāryamukhataḥ prāṃjñāḥ sidhyatyevācireṇa tu ||
ācāryarahito mantraḥ puṃso'narthasya kāraṇam || 35 ||
aparaḥ praṇavaḥ sākṣācchabdarūpaḥ sunirmalaḥ ||
paramapraṇava prāptihetutvātpraṇavo'tha vā || 3 ||
praṇavastadvācakatvena tatmāptyupāyatvācchandātmakasyāsya praṇavābhidheyatā || 3||
purā prajāpatiḥ sākṣācchraddhayā parayā saha || 4 ||
jitendriyo jitakrodho jaṭāvalkalasaṃyutaḥ || 5 ||
sadā pañcāgnimadhyasthaḥ sāmbadhyānaparāyaṇaḥ ||
tatāpa paramaṃ ghoraṃ tapaḥ saṃvatsaratrayam || 6 ||
sa punaḥ śaṃkarasyāsya prasādādamvikāpateḥ ||
pṛthivīmantarikṣaṃ ca divaṃ cāsṛjadāstikāḥ || 7 ||
trīṇi jyotīṃṣyajāyanta pṛthivyā eva tatra tu || 8 ||
ajāyatāgnirvāyuśca brāhmaṇāśvānterikṣataḥ ||
divo divākaraḥ sākṣājagaccakṣurajāyata || 9 ||
trayo vedā ajāyanta vedānāṃ prathamo'nalāva || 10 ||
yajurvedastathā vāyorādityātsāmasaṃjñitaḥ ||
vedānabhyatapattāṃśca brahmā tebhyo mahādijāḥ || 11 ||
sūtasaṃhitā 1
trīṇi śuklānyajāyanta tatra brahmavidāṃ varāḥ ||
ṛgvedādeva bhūstaddadyajurvedādbhuvastathā || 12 ||
tathā tebhyo'bhitaptebhyastrayo varṇā dvijottamāḥ || 13 ||
akāraśca tathokāro makāraśceti suvratāḥ || 14 ||
12. bhāra |
omiti prāha loko'yaṃ tena jñātasya vācakaḥ ||17||
ajñātārthe tathā'jñātamiti prāpte tu vācake ||
omiti prāha loko'yaṃ tenājñātasya vācakaḥ ||18||
omiti prāha loko'yaṃ tena saṃdigdhavācakaḥ ||19||
ākāśādipadārthānāṃ ye śabdā vācakā bhuvi ||
vinā tānakhilā śabdāloka omiti bhāṣate ||20||
ākāśādipadārthānāṃ vācakaḥ praṇavaḥ smṛtaḥ || 21 ||
sarvāvabhāsakatvena brahmaṇā sadṛśaḥ smṛtaḥ || 22 ||
akāro bindusaṃyuktaḥ śaktirasya dvijottamāḥ || 25 ||
ukāraśca makāraśca dvayaṃ bījaṃ prakīrtitam ||
mokṣārthe viniyogo'sya prokto vedāntavedibhiḥ ||26||
agniśva vāyuḥ sūryaśva varṇānāṃ munayaḥ kramāt ||
gāyatrī ca tathā triṣṭubbṛhatī ca yathākramam || 27 ||
chandāṃsi brahmavicchreṣṭhā varṇānāṃ ca yathākramam ||
brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśva varṇānāṃ devatāḥ kramāt || 28 ||
raktaṃ śuktaṃ ca kṛṣṇaṃ ca kramāddarṇā udāhṛtāḥ ||
jāgratsvamasuṣuptiśvāvasthāḥ proktā yathākramam || 29 ||
udāttapramukhā viprāḥ svarāḥ proktā manīpibhiḥ ||
ṛgyajuḥsāmasaṃjñāśca vedāḥ proktā yathākramam || 30 ||
proktaścā''havanīyāgnirvarṇānāṃ kramaśo dvijāḥ ||31||
prātarmadhyaṃdinaṃ sāyaṃ kālā uktā yathākramam ||
rajaḥ sattvaṃ tamaścaiva guṇā uktā yathākramam || 32 ||
sṛṣṭiḥ sthitiśva saṃhāraḥ kriyāḥ proktā yathākramam ||
utpattau ca sthitau nāśe viniyogā udāhṛtāḥ || 33 ||
aṅguṣṭhādikaniṣṭhāntamaṅgulīnāṃ ca saṃdhiṣu ||
kramādvarṇatrayanyāsaḥ kartavyaḥ siddhimicchatā || 34 ||
vinyastavyāśca siddhayarthamaṅgulīṣu dvijanmanā || 36 ||
japenmantravaraṃ bhaktyā lakṣāṇāṃ daśakaṃ dvijāḥ || 39 ||
ṣaṭkarmāṇi prasidhyanti tathaivāṣṭa vibhūtayaḥ || 40 ||
1 ka nyāsaḥ 1 2 ḍa. sadāśivam |
sarvavidyālayo bhūtvā yatheṣṭaṃ phalamāpnuyāt || 41 ||
sāvitrīmatha vakṣyāmi vyāhṛtyā śirasā saha ||
bhūrādivyāhṛtīnāṃ tu munayaḥ parikīrtitāḥ || 1 ||
kaśyapaśvāṅgirāśveti krameṇa munipuṅgavāḥ || 2 ||
vyāhṛtīnāṃ krameṇaiva chandāṃsi kathitāni tu ||
devīgāyatramādyaṃ syāduṣṇihā tadanantaram || 3 ||
anuṣṭubbṛhatī paṅaktistriṣṭup ca jagatī tathā ||
agnirvāyustathā'rkaśva vāgīśo varuṇastathā || 4 ||
vyāhṛtīnāṃ tu sarvatra viniyogaḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 5 ||
tripadā sā tu sāvitrī ṣaḍbhirvarṇaiścatuṣpadā ||
jape sā tripadā jñeyā pūjāyāṃ sā catuṣpadā || 7 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
sāvitrī tripadā jñeyā paṭṭūkṣiḥ pañcaśīrṣakā ||
agnivarṇamukhā śuklā puṇḍarīkadalekṣaṇā || 10 ||
ṛgyajuḥsāmarūpāśca pādā asyāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||
pūrvā dikprathamā kukṣirdvitīyā dakṣiṇā matā || 11 ||
paścimā diktṛtīyā ca caturthī cottarā matā ||
ūrdhvā dikpañcamī kukṣiḥ ṣaṣṭhayadho dikprakīrtitā || 12 ||
aṣṭādaśa purāṇāni nābhirasyā munīśvarāḥ ||
jagaccharīraṃ sāvitryā jākāśamudarāntaram || 13 ||
bāhavo nyāyaśāstraṃ tu karṇau sāṃkhyadayaṃ tathā || 14 ||
śikṣādyaṅgāni śīrṣāṇi vaktramagnirmahādyutiḥ ||
mīmāṃsā lakṣaṇaṃ tasyāśveśa cā''tharvaṇī śrutiḥ ||15||
brahmā mūrdhā śikhā rudro viṣṇurātmā prakīrtitaḥ ||
tasyāḥ sūkṣmaśarīraṃ ca śāstraṃ vedāntasaṃjñitam || 16 ||
antaryāmī śivaḥ sākṣātsāmbaścandrārdhaśekharaḥ ||
svaśarīre tu sāvitrīṃ vinyasedakṣarakramāt || 17 ||
pādāṅguṣṭhe tu gulphe tu jaṅghe jānupradeśake ||
ūrudeśe ca guhye ca vṛṣaṇe ca tathaiva ca || 18 ||
kaṇṭhe ca vadane tālau nāsikāyāṃ ca cakṣupoḥ || 19 ||
uttare ca tathā mūrdhni nyāsaḥ samyakprakīrtitaḥ || 20 ||
sūtasaṃhitā 1
vidyuddarṇanibhaḥ sākṣādaṣṭamaḥ paribhāṣitaḥ ||
navamastārakāvarṇo daśamaḥ kṛṣṇavarṇakaḥ || 23 ||
śuklavarṇaḥ pītavarṇo raktavarṇaḥ paraḥ smṛtaḥ || 24 ||
śuklavarṇaḥ paro varṇaḥ padmarāgaprabhaḥ paraḥ || 25 ||
tatparaḥ śaśisaṃkāśaḥ pāṇḍuraḥ paramo mataḥ ||
tatparo ratnagaurābha indranīlasamo'tha vā || 26 ||
nīlotpaladalaprakhyo varṇastatparamastathā || 27 ||
śaṅkhakundenduvarṇābhaḥ sākṣāddarṇaḥ paraḥ smṛtaḥ ||
tatparo dīpasaṃkāśaḥ kramādvarṇāḥ prakīrtitāḥ || 28 ||
keciddarṇāstu sāvitryā mahāpātakanāśanāḥ ||
upapātakapāpānāṃ varṇāḥ kecana bādhakāḥ ||
kecana kṣudrapāpānāṃ nāśakāḥ syurna saṃśayaḥ || 29 ||
nānatoyasamaṃ dānaṃ na cāhiṃsāparaṃ tapaḥ ||
na sāvitrīsamaṃ japyaṃ na vyāhṛtisamaṃ hutam ||30||
nānatopeti || 30 ||
pracodayātprerayecca tasya devasya suvratāḥ || 31 ||
svamāyāśaktisaṃbhinnaṃ śivarudrādisaṃjñitam ||
nīlagrīvaṃ virūpākṣaṃ sāmvamūrtyapalakṣitam || 34 ||
ādityadevatāyāstu prerakaṃ parameśvaram || || 35 ||
ādityenāparijñātaṃ vayaṃ dhīmahyupāsmahe ||
sāvitryāḥ kathito hyarthaḥ saṃgraheṇa mayā''dāt || 36 ||
sarvakāmasamṛddhiḥ syānnātra kāryā vicāraṇā ||
karīpacūrṇato hutvā sarpipā saha mānavaḥ || 42 ||
gavāṃ goṣṭhe sahasraṃ tu bahukṣirāṃ labheta gām ||
śālyāstaṇḍulahomena kanyāsiddhirbhaviṣyati || 43 ||
śolībījasya homena prajāmiṣṭāmavāpnuyāt ||
sāvitryā jalamādāya jatvā cāṣṭasahasrakam || 44 ||
śrīharī japeearttyuvināśane || 45 ||
ghṛtāhāro japeddidyāṃ labhate nātra saṃśayaḥ ||
nābhimātre jale sthitvā japellakṣaṃ samāhitaḥ || 46 ||
akaṇṭakaṃ mahārājyaṃ labhate nātra saṃśayaḥ ||
palāśapuṣpahomena mahatīṃ śriyamaśnute || 47 ||
vetasairjayādau dṛṣṭiṃ śīghramavāpnuyāt ||
madhuhomena viprendrā rājānaṃ vaśamāyāt || 48 ||
śatroḥ pratikṛtiṃ bhūmāvālikhyā''khyāṃ ca tahṛdi ||
saṃmākramya tu pādaina japecchaṃ rvinaśyati || 53 ||
karmasu prayoktavyamityairthaḥ || 54 ||
pañcagavyena vā hutvā tilairvā śāntimāpnuyāt ||55||
udumbarabhavāśvatthaigegajāśvāmayakṣayaḥ || 56 ||
payasā''jyena vā hutvā śāntiḥ sarvacatuṣpadām ||
śāntaye sarvadoṣāṇāṃ jānumātre jale japet || 57 ||
abhimantrya sitaṃ bhasma nyaseḍūtādiśāntaye || 58 ||
abhīṣṭaṃ sarvamāproti nātra saṃdehakāraṇam || 59 ||
7. 8. gha. ahaṃkāraḥ pumānproktaḥ |
7 adhyāyaḥ ] '
dhyāyetsāmyaṃ mahādevaṃ saṃsārāmayabheṣajam || 3 ||
athavā prāṇasaṃcāraḥ sakāraḥ parikīrtitaḥ ||
hakāro'pānasaṃcāro dehe dehabhṛtāṃ sadā || 5 ||
yo vijānāti pāpāni buddhipūrvakṛtāni ca ||
tasya naśyanti sarvāṇi nātra kāryā vicāraṇā || 8 ||
haṃsayoḥ śabalaṃ hitvā padayoḥ sadditīyayoḥ ||
pūrṇo'hamevaṃ jānīyādbodhamātrasvabhāvataḥ || 13 ||
ahamavyabhicāryeva sākṣitvādvyabhicāriṇām || 15 ||
jñātamajñātamapyarthaṃ sadā'haṃ veda kevalaḥ ||
so'rtho māṃ na vijānāti tato'vicchinnacetanaḥ || 16 ||
ciṃjjaḍaspā''tmanaḥ śeṣaḥ syājjaḍatvāviśepāccharāvādīnāmapi cicchapatvena
bhidyate cedaciccitsyāccito'cittvaṃ virudhyate || 18 ||
pūrṇo'haṃ sarvasākṣitvātsarvadā paramārthataḥ ||
apūrṇo yugapatsarvaṃ na vijānāti kaścana || 22 ||
saṃsāravarjitaḥ sākṣātsarvadā parameśvaraḥ ||
ahaṃ saṃsārasākṣitvāttathā saṃsāravarjitaḥ || 23 ||
evaṃ vākyānusāriṇyā yuktyā''cāryapuraḥsaram ||
ahaṃ sa so'hameveti vijānīyādvicakṣaṇaḥ || 24 ||
tparthaḥ || 24 ||
sa eva brahmavinmukhyo netaro'jñānamohitaḥ || 25 ||
evaṃbhūtaṃ parijñānaṃ yasya jātaṃ yadā bhuvi ||
tadaiva tasya saṃsāravināśo nāsti saṃśayaḥ || 26 ||
asyāśca japamātreṇa dīrghāyuṣyamavāpnuyāt ||
ārogyaṃ vijayaṃ vidyāmavāpnoti na saṃśayaḥ || 29 ||
haṃsa haṃseti yo brūyātsarvadā śiva eva saḥ || 30 ||
jātā haṃsavidheyamacirādeva siddhidā || 21 ||
nābhikande samau kṛtvā prāṇāpānau samāhitaḥ || 32 ||
dīpākāraṃ mahādevaṃ jvalantaṃ nābhimadhyame || 33 ||
yo dadāti mahāvidyāṃ haṃsākhyāṃ parameśvarīm ||
tasya dāsyaṃ sadā kuryācchūddhayā parayā saha || 37 ||
dadātīti || 37 ||
śubhaṃ vā'śubhamanyadvā yaduktaṃ guruṇā bhuvi ||
tatkuryādavicāreṇa śiṣyaḥ saṃtoṣasaṃyuktaḥ || 38 ||
haṃsavidyāmimāṃ labdhvā guroḥ śuśrūṣayā naraḥ ||
ātmānamātmanā sākṣādbrahma buddhvā suniścalaḥ||39||
payeṇāntaḥkaraṇena || 39 ||
dehajātyādisaṃbandhānvarṇāśramasamanvitān || 40 ||
vedāśāstrāṇi cānyāni pādapāṃsumiva tyajet ||
na guruṃ saṃtyajennityaṃ jānannasya kṛtaṃ naraḥ || 41 ||
atha ṛṣpādyānāha — ṛpirbrahmeti || 2 ||
śaktirmāheśvarī sā ca bhuvaneśākṣaraṃ bhavet ||
vījaṃ māyāviśiṣṭastu śivaḥ pūrvoktalakṣaṇaḥ || 3 ||
aṅguṣṭhādikaniṣṭhāntaṃ vinyasedakṣaraṃ kramāt || 4 ||
punaḥ pañcākṣareṇaiva pañcāṅgaṃ visanyetkramāt || 5 ||
vakāraṃ pañcamaṃ vidyādyakāraṃ paṣṭhameva ca ||
itthaṃ paḍakṣaraṃ vidyājjābālopaniṣadgatam || 7||
asaṃpṛktyā śivasyāyaṃ śivaśabdastu vācakaḥ ||
namaḥ śabdo namaskāravācakaḥ parikīrtitaḥ || 9 ||
prahṛtālakṣaṇaḥ prokto namaskāraḥ purātanaiḥ ||
prahnatā nāma jīvasya śivātsatyādilakṣaṇāt || 10 ||
saṃbandha eva tenaiva so'pi tādātmyalakṣaṇaḥ || 11 ||
nityasiddha ḥ śivaḥ sākṣātsvarūpaḥ sarvadehinām ||
tasmādubhutsorjīvasya nopādeyaṃ hitaṃ sadā || 12 ||
evaṃ vidyānnakārārthaṃ makārārtha udīryate || 13 ||
tasmācchivasya pūrṇasya praṇavo vācakaḥ smṛtaḥ ||16||
vācyavācakabhāvaśva lakṣyalakṣaṇatā'pi ca ||
anyonyatā'pi nāstyeva paramārthanirūpaṇe || 17 ||
asti nāsti mṛpā bhāti na bhātītyādi māyayā || 18 ||
māyātatkāryamapyasmācchivātsatyādilakṣaṇāva ||
pratyakṣasiddhānnāstyeva paramārthanirūpaṇe || 19 ||
atha kiṃ bahunoktena śivādanyanna vidyate || 20 ||
śivasvarūpamevā''huridaṃ sarva vicakṣaṇāḥ ||
sarvasvarūpamajñānādṛśyate na tu vastutaḥ || 21 ||
vedāḥ sarve purāṇāni smṛtayo bhārataṃ tathā || 22 ||
anyānyapi ca śāstrāṇi tathā tarkāśva sarvaśaḥ ||
śaivāgamāśca vividhā āgamā vaiṣṇavā api || 23 ||
asminnarthe svasaṃvedye paryavasyanti nānyathā || 24 ||
srānaṃ triṣavaṇaṃ kṛtvā bhasmanā śākabhojanaḥ || 27 ||
phalamūlāśano vā'pi haviṣyāśī yathāvalam ||
parvatāgre nadītīre sāgarānte śivālaye || 28 ||
samāhitamanā bhūtvā sukhamāsanamāsthitaḥ || 29 ||
devatāṃ caṃ tathā śaktiṃ vījaṃ smṛtvā manorapi || 30 ||
karanyāsaṃ punaḥ kṛtvā tathā'ṅganyāsameva ca ||
pañcāṅgamapi vinyasya guruṃ smṛtvā'bhivandya ca ||31||
hṛtpuṇḍarīkamadhye tu somasūryāgnimaṇḍale ||
vidyullekheva kalyāṇaṃ jvalantaṃ vahnirūpiṇam || 32 ||
śivaṃ dhyātvā japenmantraṃ lakṣāṇāṃ pad samāhitaḥ ||
tarpayelakṣamekaṃ tu juhuyāttu sahasrakam || 33 ||
tataḥ sidhyati mantro'sya bhuktimuktiphalapradaḥ || 34 ||
athavā sāmvamīśānaṃ śrīsadāśivameva ca ||
nṛtyamānaṃ tathā deveṃ dhyātvā mantraṃ tu sādhayet ||35||
athavā prākṛtaṃ bhāvaṃ svīyamutsṛjya sarvadā ||
śivo'hamiti saṃcintya sādhayedidamuttamam || 36 ||
nityaṃ dvādaśasāhasraṃ japeddhatayā samāhitaḥ || 37 ||
samyagjñānapṭhavaṃ labdhvā saṃsārābdhi tariṣyati ||
lakṣapañcāśataṃ japtvā kāraṇeśvaramāpnuyāt || 38 ||
lakṣāṇāṃ tu śataṃ japtvā sākṣādrudratvamāpnuyāt ||
aśītilakṣaṃ japtvā tu naro viṣṇutvamāpnuyāt || 39 ||
catvāriṃśatibhirlakṣairvirāḍātmānamāpnuyāt || 40 ||
viṃśalakṣajapenaiva dīrghamāyuravāśayāt ||
viniyogaḥ samākhyātaḥ pūjā devasya kīrtyate || 41 ||
arghyaṃ tataḥ paraṃ dadyātpādyaṃ caiva tataḥ param || 44 ||
vāso dadyātpunaryajñopavītaṃ bhūpaṇāni ca || 45 ||
paḍakṣareṇa mantreṇa sarvaṃ kuryādvicakṣaṇaḥ || 46 ||
sarvamuktaṃ samāsena narāṇāṃ bhuktimuktaye || 48 ||
paḍakṣareṇa sarvāṇi sidhyantyeva na saṃśayaḥ || 49 ||
dhyānayajñamathedānīṃ pravakṣyāmi samāsataḥ ||
śṛṇuta śraddhayā yūyaṃ bhuktimuktiphalapradam || 1 ||
na svarūpeṇa sākṣitvādātmatvādviṣayitvataḥ || 2 ||
varadābhayahastā ca vicitra mukuṭojjvalā || 4 ||
sarvalakṣaṇasaṃpannā sarvābharaṇabhūṣitā ||
svasvarūpānusaṃdhānapramodādeva kevalāva || 5 ||
mahātāṇḍavasaṃyuktā brahmaviṣṇuśivādibhiḥ ||
dhyeyā''dyantavinirmuktā yā mūrtiḥ śrutidarśitā || 6 ||
saivāsādhāraṇā mūrtiḥ parātparatarasya tu ||
imāṃ te paramāṃ muktiṃ muktiṃ ca prāpnuvanti hi || 7 ||
jñānājñānamahāmāyālakṣaṇāvidyayā saha ||
abhedena sthitaṃ viprāḥ parātparataraṃ padam || 8 ||
samapradhānarūpeṇāpyādareṇa manīṣibhiḥ || 9 ||
jāḍyākārastu yaḥ śaktestenābhinnaṃ paraṃ padam ||
svapradhānādirūpeṇa tridhopāsyaṃ vicakṣaṇaiḥ || 12 ||
tathā śaktestu yo jñānākārastenaikatāṃ gatam ||
paratattvaṃ tridhopāsyaṃ parijñānavatāṃ varāḥ || 13 ||
māyākāraikatāpannamapi tattvaṃ manīṣibhiḥ || 14 ||
abhedena sthitaṃ brahma tridhopāsyaṃ manīṣibhiḥ || 15 ||
anye ca śakterākārā ye vidyante vicakṣaṇāḥ ||
tairapyekatvamāpannaṃ tattvaṃ taddanmanīṣibhiḥ || 16 ||
īkṣaṇopādhisaṃpannaṃ paratattvamapi dvijāḥ ||
svapradhānādirūpeṇa tridhopāsyamatipriyāt || 17 ||
te jagannāśasargādeḥ kartāraḥ kāryarūpiṇaḥ ||
upāsyāstrividhā nityaṃ te'pi svaṃ svamupādhibhiḥ||20||
agnyādityādidevā ye nihīnā madhyamāḥ parāḥ ||
te ca brahmātmanā nityamupāsyā eva sādaram || 22 ||
śabdasparśādisaṃjñā ye padārthāḥ pañca te'pi ca ||
upāsyā brahmarūpeṇa mahāprājñairmanīpibhiḥ || 23 ||
ākāśādīni bhūtāni yāni tāni manīṣibhiḥ ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyāni mahātmabhiḥ || 24 ||
bhautikā aṇḍabhedāśva brahmarūpeṇa sādaram ||
cintanīyāśca vidyadbhirvedavedāntapāragāḥ || 25 ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyā eva sūribhiḥ || 26 ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyā munisattamaiḥ || 27 ||
merumandārapūrvāśca parvatā vividhā dvijāḥ ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyā vedavittamāḥ || 28 ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyāḥ puruṣottamaiḥ || 29 ||
vāpīkūpataḍāgādyā api vedaparāyaṇāḥ ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyāḥ puruṣādhikaiḥ || 30 ||
tāni brahmatayā nityamupāsyāni tapodhanaiḥ || 31 ||
dhyātavyā eva kevalam || 32 ||
anāgatādayaḥ kālā upāsyā brahmarūpataḥ || 33 ||
aṇḍajaṃ jārajaṃ caiva svedajaṃ codvijaṃ tathā ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyā mohavarjitaiḥ || 34 ||
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyāḥ śūdrā api ca saṃkarāḥ ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyā eva sūribhiḥ || 35 ||
āśramā brahmacaryādyāstadācārā api dvijāḥ ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyāḥ paramāstikaiḥ || 36 ||
mahāpātakapūrvāṇi pāpāni subahūni ca ||
brahmarūpatayā nityamupāsyāni mahattamaiḥ || 37 ||
te'pi brahmatayā nityamupāsyāḥ paṇḍitottamaiḥ ||38||
brahmarūpatayā sarvamupāsyaṃ satyavādibhiḥ || 39 ||
brahmarūpatayā sarvamupāsyaṃ cetanottamaiḥ || 40 ||
avandhyāśca tathā vandhyā vādāśca vividhā api ||
brahmarūpatayā sarvamupāsyaṃ vākyavedibhiḥ || 43 ||
dhyānayajñasya māhātmyaṃ kalpānāṃ koṭikoṭibhiḥ ||
mayā matto'dhikairanyairapi vaktuṃ na śakyate || 46 ||
pāyasānnaṃ parityajya bhakṣayanti mahāviṣam || 47 ||
aśvamedhādayo yajñā aśeṣā vedadarśitāḥ ||
munīndrā dhyānayajñasya kalāṃ nārhanti poḍaśīm ||49||
dhyānayajñaikaniṣṭhasya na kiṃcidapi durlabham || 50 ||
dhyānayajñaparāṇāṃ tu prasādaṃ kurute śivaḥ ||
śivo'pi sākṣātsarvajñaḥ saṃsāravinivartakaḥ || 51 ||
kurudhvaṃ vedavinmukhyā dhyānayajñamaśaṅkitāḥ || 52 ||
svarūpamekaṃ vijñānaṃ śivasya paramātmanaḥ ||
tadeva māyātatkāryabhedena bahudhā bhavet || 3 ||
māyākāreṇa saṃvaddhaṃ jaḍaśakteḥ śivasya tu ||
jñānamīśvarasaṃjñaṃ ca niyantu jagato bhavet || 4 ||
śakteravidyākāreṇa saṃvaddhaṃ jīvasaṃjñitam ||
arthato mukhyamekaṃ tu jñānamanyatpratītitaḥ || 5 ||
sthūlasūkṣmaśarīrābhyāmavacchinnaṃ pratītitaḥ || 6 ||
svapracārāśrayaṃ cittaṃ jīvarūpaprakāśakam ||
jñātṛtva heturjīvasya duḥkhitvādeśva kāraṇam || 7 ||
pramāṇabhrāntisaṃdehādyākāreṇa munīśvarāḥ ||
bahurūpaṃ bhavecittaṃ kālakarmavipākataḥ || 8 ||
aduṣṭakaraṇotpannaṃ vijñānaṃ munipuṅgavāḥ ||
pramāṇajñānamityuktaṃ munibhiḥ sūkṣmadarśibhiḥ || 10 ||
duṣṭakāraṇavijñānaṃ bhrāntijñānaṃ pracakṣate ||
koṭiyāvalambi syātsaṃdehajñānamāstikāḥ || 11 ||
sa eva niśvayaḥ proktaḥ samyagdarśanatatparaiḥ || 12 ||
jñānasya tena saṃvandhaḥ prāmāṇyaṃ kathitaṃ mayā ||
pramāṇajñānasāmagryaḥ paṇmayā'bhihitā budhāḥ || 13 ||
tatraikā'bhāvavijñānasāmagrī kathitā dvijāḥ ||
anyā tu bhāvavijñānasāmagrī parikīrtitā || 14 ||
vyāptijanyaparijñānamanumānamitīṣyate || 16 ||
mānamiti tatvavidaḥ || 16 ||
sādṛśyahetujaṃ jñānamupamānamudāhṛtam ||
arthāpattiriti proktaṃ viprā anupapattijam || 17 ||
. sūtasaṃhitā |
sparthaḥ || 17 ||
tātpayoṃpetaśabdotthajñānaṃ śābdamudāhṛtam ||
śabdastu brahmavicchreṣṭhā strividhaḥ parikīrtitaḥ || 18 ||
vākyāni ceti tatrāpi keṣāṃcidra dvijapuṅgavāḥ || 19 ||
ityavadhāraṇārthaḥ || 20 ||
arthānāmapi keṣāṃcitpramāṇāni pradīpavat || 21 ||
bhavantyekākṣarāṇyeva padāni dijapuṅgavāḥ ||
akṣarāṇi ca saṃbhūya padāni syustathaiva ca || 22 ||
pradhānaṃ guṇabhūtaṃ ca dvividhaṃ vākyamīritam || 23 ||
guṇabhṛtaṃ tu yadvākyaṃ tadvāntarasaṃjñitam || 24 ||
padāni śaktyā svārthānāṃ vācakāni tathaiva ca || 25 ||
tātparyādeva vākyāni svārthānāṃ bodhakāni ca ||
tātparye tu dvidhā viprāḥ proktaṃ vākyaviśāradaiḥ ||26||
mahātātparyaśeṣaṃ syādavāntarasamāhvayam || 27 ||
tatraivaṃ sati vākyāni kānicitpaṇḍitottamāḥ ||
niṣedharūpāṇyeva syustathā viprāstu kānicit || 28||
vidhirūpāṇi cānyāni kānici dvijapuṅgavāḥ ||
siddhārthabodhakānyeva tatraivaṃ sati vāḍavāḥ || 29 ||
- 10 adhyāyaḥ ]
sūtasaṃditā |
pratyakṣādipramāṇāni pañca ca brāhmaṇottamāḥ || 32 ||
parāgarthaikaniṣṭhatvātmatyaktvādātmavastunaḥ || 33 ||
pratyagbhūtaḥ śivo jñātuṃ na śakyaḥ sarvajantubhiḥ || 34 ||
pratyagātmā śivaḥ sākṣāna parāgartha āstikāḥ ||
parācīnasya sarvasya hyanātmatvapradarśanāt || 35 ||
sidvārthavodhakaṃ vākyaṃ laukikaṃ kiṃcidāstikāḥ ||
anātmaviṣayaṃ tena śivo jñātuṃ na śakyate || 36 ||
pratyagrūpe śive sākṣātpramāṇaṃ bhavati dvijāḥ ||
vedāntānāṃ mahāvākyaṃ pratyagbrahmakatārthagam || 37 ||
pe vevamātmanaḥ saṃsāraḥ svābhāvika ityāhustepāṃ ghaṭādidharmaspa
rūpāderdharmiṇā ghaṭādinā sadaiva nāśo dṛṣṭa iti dharmabhūtasaṃsāranivṛttau
yato ghaṭādernāśastu dṛṣṭo viprā anātmanaḥ ||41||
āhuścidrūpato bhedaśvito nāstyeva sarvathā || 44 ||
vaṭādīnāṃ tu caityānāmanātmatvasya darśanāva ||
mātmano'pi khato bhedamāhuḥ kecinmunīśvarāḥ ||46||
bhedasākṣī śivo hyātmā kathaṃ bhinno bhaveddijāḥ ||47||
nirastaśvā''tmabhedastu ghaṭādīnāṃ bhidā'pi ca ||
bhrāntisiddhā na satyoktā tarkataśva pramāṇataḥ ||51||
ghaṭādīnāṃ bhidā tāvanna bhrāntaiva pratītitaḥ
pratītyā satyarūpaiva vyavahāre munīśvarāḥ || 52 ||
sarvabhūteṣu cā''tmānaṃ sarvabhūtāni cā''tmani ||
saṃpaśyannātmayājī syātsvārājyamadhigacchati || 60 ||
sarvabhūtāni saṃpaśyatrātmanyeva munīśvarāḥ ||
saṃsārasāgarādasmāduttīrṇaḥ syānna saṃśayaḥ || 61 ||
sūtasaṃditā |
dvaitavijñānamāsādya muktiṃ vāñchanti ye narāḥ ||
te mahāmohasaṃsārasarpadaṣṭā na saṃśayaḥ || 63 ||
ātmayāthātmyavijñānayajñaṃ muktvā narādhamāḥ ||
kriyārūpeṣu yajñeṣu yatante māyayā'nṛtāḥ || 64 ||
te mahātamasā sarve paśyantyeva raviṃ vinā || 65 ||
jñānayajñoḍupenaiva brāhmaṇo vā'ntyajo'pi vāṃ ||
saṃsārasāgaraṃ tīrtvā muktipāraṃ hi gacchati || 66 ||
aho māheśvarajñānaṃ yajñavaibhavamāstikāḥ ||
avijñāya narā loke yatante sāravarjite || 67 ||
kiṃ punarmānavā viprāḥ śivo jānāti sarvavida ||68||
prasādādeva rudrasya jānanti jñānavaibhavam || 69 ||
prasādahīnaiḥ pāpiṣṭhairmanuṣyaitrīhmaṇottamāḥ ||
jñānayajñaḥ parijñātuṃ na śakyaḥ sarvasādhanaiḥ || 70 ||
jñānayajñaikaniṣṭhānāṃ nāvāpyaṃ vidyate kvacit ||
na yaṃ vidyate sarva brahmarūpeṇa bhāti hi || 71 ||
munibhiśva tathā devaistathā'nyairapi jantubhiḥ || 72 ||
kathaṃcicchakyate vaktuṃ satyameva na saṃśayaḥ || 73 ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 2 ||
dharmādharmaphalāstitvajñānaṃ yeṣāṃ hṛdi sthitam ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 3 ||
śrutismṛtyādiviśvāso yeṣāmasti sadā hṛdi ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 4 ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 5 ||
yamataskiṃkarāstitvajñānaṃ yeṣāṃ hṛdi sthitam ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 6 ||
bhūtapretādisadbhāvajñānaṃ yeṣāṃ hṛdi sthitam ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 7 ||
yakṣarakṣādisadbhāvo yeṣāṃ bhāti pramāṇataḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 8 ||
munīnāmastitābuddhiryeṣāmasti munīśvarāḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 9 ||
indrādidevatāstittvaṃ yeṣāṃ citte prakāśate ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 10 ||
brahmā viśiṣṭo devānāmiti jānanti ye janāḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 11 ||
brahmaṇo viṣṇumutkṛṣṭaṃ ye jānanti pramāṇataḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 12 ||
viṣṇorviśiṣṭaṃ rudra ye vijānanti pramāṇataḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 13 ||
rudrādīśvaramutkṛṣṭaṃ ye jānanti suniścitam ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 14 ||
īśvarādadhiko bhāti yeṣāṃ citte sadāśivaḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 15 ||
sadāśivādapi śreṣṭhaṃ brahmāṇaṃ ye janā viduḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 16 ||
brahmaṇaḥ paramaṃ sākṣāddiṣṇuṃ jānanti ye janāḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 17 ||
viṣṇostu paramaṃ sākṣādudaṃ jānanti ye janāḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 18 ||
īkṣitāraṃ paraṃ rudrādye vijānanti mānavāḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 19 ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ ||20||
kāraṇaṃ brahma sarveṣāṃ viśiṣṭamiti ye viduḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ ||21||
kāraṇatvopalakṣyaṃ ye sarvotkṛṣṭaṃ śivaṃ viduḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ ||22||
dehādanyatayā jīvaṃ ye jānanti pramāṇataḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 24 ||
prāṇādanyatayā''tmānaṃ ye jānanti pramāṇataḥ ||
ve'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ ||25||
kṣaṇapradhvaṃsivijñānādātmānaṃ ye paraṃ viduḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 28 ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ ||29||
cittādanyatayā''tmānaṃ ye jānanti pramāṇataḥ ||
te'pi vijñānasaṃpannā iti me niścitā matiḥ ||30||
syābuddhisaṃjñā ca yadā pravetti jñātāramātmānamahaṃkṛtiḥ syāt ||
sa evā''tmā na taddṛśyaṃ dṛśyaṃ tasminprakalpitam || 32 ||
tridhāmasākṣiṇaṃ saṃtyajñānānandādilakṣaṇam ||
tvamahaṃśabdalakṣyārthamasaktaṃ sarvadoṣataḥ || 33 ||
jñātājñātadvayādanyaṃ jñātājñātasya bhāsakam ||
pramāṇabhrāntivṛttīnāmagamyaṃ tatprakāśakam || 34 ||
§ q. °¤¿ à° |
nvarvartinamātmānaṃ ye jānanti te'pītyādi pūrvavat || 35 ||
uktalakṣaṇamātmānamuktalakṣaṇamīśvaram ||
ekaṃ paśyanti ye viprāstarkataśca pramāṇataḥ || 36 ||
na paṭhitavyamasajjanasaṃsadi || 38 ||
bhūyo'pi jñānayajñaṃ tu pravakṣyāmi samāsataḥ ||
munayaḥ parayā bhaktyā śṛṇutātīva śobhanam || 1 ||
amacyutātmabhāvena saṃsthitaṃ sarvadeva tu || 2 ||
sarvajñatvādikā stambaparyantā māyayaiva tu || 6 ||
utkarṣaścāpakarṣaśca māyayā tepu kalpitaḥ ||
niyantṛtvaniyamyatvādyākārāśca prakalpitāḥ ||7||
mahadādijagacchūnyaparyantaṃ parikalpitam || 8 ||
utkarṣaścāpakarṣaśca jagatyapi munīśvarāḥ ||
kalpitaḥ sarvatodriktaṃ vyavahāre tu māyayā || 9 ||
varṇāśramāstathā viprā varṇasāṃkaryameva ca ||
tamīśva vibhāgena māyayaiva prakalpitāḥ || 10 ||
vidhayaśca niṣedhāśva śrutismṛtyādirūpiṇaḥ ||
māyayā devadevasya satyavatparikalpitāḥ || 12 ||
kalpitāni mahāmohādvahmaṇo na svabhāvataḥ || 13 ||
rāgadveṣādayo doṣāḥ śāntidānyādayo guṇāḥ ||
api māheśvaraṃ jñānaṃ māyayaiva prakalpitam || 14 ||
tattatsarva mahādevamāyayā parikalpitam || 16 ||
sarvajñatvādikā bhedāḥ stambāntā ye prakalpitāḥ ||
te śivādanyato nityaṃ na santyeva nirūpaṇe || 18 ||
varṇāśramādayo bhāvā māyayā ye prakalpitāḥ ||
te'pi śaṃbho bhedena santi samyanirūpaṇe || 22 ||
te'pi śaṃbhorna bhedena santi samyanirūpaṇe || 23 ||
vidhayaśva niṣedhāśca māyayā ye prakalpitāḥ ||
ve'pi śaṃbhorna bhedena santi samyanirūpaṇe || 24 ||
dharmādharmādirūpeṇa māyayā ye prakalpitāḥ ||
te'pi śaṃbhorna bhedena santi samyanirūpaṇe ||25||
rāgadveṣādirūpāśca māyayā ye prakalpitāḥ ||
te'pi śaṃbhorna bhedena santi samyanirūpaṇe || 26 ||
vaidikāstāntrikā mārgā apabhraṃśāśca ye dvijāḥ ||
te'pi śaṃbhorna bhedena santi samyanirūpaṇe || 27 ||
tattacchaṃbhorna bhedena vidyate sūkṣmadarśane || 28 ||
ataśca saṃkṣepamimaṃ śṛṇudhvaṃ
na devadevātpṛthagasti kiṃcit || 29 ||
bhūyo'pi jñānayajñaṃ tu pravakṣyāmi samāsataḥ ||
guhyādguhyatamaṃ sūkṣmaṃ śṛṇuta śradvayā dvijāḥ || 1 ||
cinmātrāśrayamāyāyāḥ śaktyākāre dvijottamāḥ ||
anupraviṣṭā yā saṃvinnirvikalpā svayaṃprabhā || 2 ||
sadākārā parānandā saṃsārocchedakāriṇī ||
sā śivā paramā devī śivābhinnā śivaṃkarī || 3 ||
16. 'tadaśāyā |
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 4 ||
sarvajñatvaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 5 ||
īkṣitṛtvaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 6 ||
yastu rudratvamāpannaḥ śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 7 ||
yastu viṣṇutvamāpannaḥ śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hono nirarthakaḥ || 8||
yastu brahmatvamāpannaḥ śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 9 ||
sadāśivatvaṃ yaḥ prāptaḥ śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchatistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||10||
īśvaratvaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 11||
sūtrātmatvaṃ tathā yastu śivaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||13||
virārūpaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||14||
svarārūpaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||15||
samrāḍrūpaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 16 ||
indrādilokapālānāṃ rūpaṃ yaḥ prāptavāśivaḥ ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 17 ||
indrādilokapālānāmityādyā upādhayaḥ spaṣṭāḥ || 17 ||
devādīnāṃ gato yastu rūpaṃ śaṃmurupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 18 ||
manuṣyatvaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasthāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 19 ||
tiryagādisvarūpaṃ yaḥ śivaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||20||
joṣadhīnāṃ svarūpaṃ yaḥ śivaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||21||
vanaspatīnāṃ rūpaṃ yaḥ śivaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||22||
bhakṣyabhojyādirūpaṃ yaḥ śivaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 23 ||
nadīnadādirūpaṃ yaḥ śivaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 24 ||
parvatādisvarūpaṃ yaḥ śirvaḥ prāpta upādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 25 ||
samudrarūpaṃ yaḥ prāptaḥ śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ || 26 ||
vidyudrapaṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchattistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||27||
sarvākāraṃ gato yastu śivaḥ sākṣādupādhinā ||
sā tasyāpi bhavecchaktistayā hīno nirarthakaḥ ||28||
epā sā sākṣiṇī śaktiḥ śaṃkarasyāpi śaṃkarī ||
śivābhinnā tathā hīnaḥ śivaḥ sākṣānnirarthakaḥ || 29 ||
umāśaṃkarayorbhedaṃ ye paśyanti narādhamāḥ ||
adhomukhordhvapādāste yāsyanti narakārṇavam || 31 ||
yathā mātāpitṛbhyāṃ tu vardhante mānavā bhuvi ||
tathaivā''bhyāmidaṃ kṛtsnaṃ vardhate nātra saṃśayaḥ || 32 ||
lakṣmīvāgādirūpaipā śivā khalu munīśvarāḥ ||
nartakīvānayā sarvamacirādeva sidhyati || 35 ||
śaivā bhāgavatāsteṣāmupabhedāvalambinaḥ ||
asyā ārādhanenaiva labhante'bhīpsitaṃ phalam ||38||
asyā ārādhanenaiva labhante'bhīpsitaṃ phalam || 39 ||
yathā yathā śivāmetāṃ yo vā ko vāssdareṇa tu ||
ārādhayati so'bhīṣṭaṃ labhate phalamāstikāḥ || 40 ||
karuṇāsāgarāmetāṃ yaḥ pūjayati śāṃkarīm ||
kiṃ na sidhyati tasyeṣṭaṃ tasyā eva prasādataḥ || 41 ||
śivāmetāmumāmenāṃ jaḍaśaktiṃ tathaiva ca ||
jaḍakārya jagajjīvaṃ tepāṃ bhedaṃ tathaiva ca || 42 ||
anyañcāstitayā bhātaṃ tathā nāstītiśabditam ||
sarva pūrṇa śivaṃ paśyansvayaṃ pūrṇaḥ śivo bhavet || 43 ||
pūrṇameva svakaṃ rūpamapūrṇa āti māyayā ||
pūrṇarūpatayā māyāṃ paśyanpūrṇo bhavetsvayam || 44 ||
svapūrṇātmātirekeṇa jagajjīveśvarādayaḥ ||
na santi nāsti māyā ca tadviśuddhātmavedanam ||45 ||
svapūrṇātmaśivānandaniṣṭhāmāsādya mānavaḥ ||
tadeva labhate muktiṃ svapūrṇātmaśivātmikām || 46 ||
svapūrṇātmaśivānandaprakāśabalataḥ pumān ||
svacchandaṃ vartate loke ko vā tasya nivārakaḥ ||47||
svapūrṇātmaśivajñānī svacchandaṃ vartate tathā || 48 ||
saṃsārastasya muktirvā kathaṃ sidhyati yoginaḥ ||49||
saṃsāro vā vimuktirvā yasya bhāti munīśvarāḥ ||
tasyaiva hi niṣedhāśva vidhayaśva na yoginaḥ || 50 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
spṛśyate mṛttikā vipraiścaṇḍālairapi kevalā ||
saiva kumbhādirūpeṇa nīcairna spṛśyate yathā || 51 ||
nindyānindyatayā'jñasya bhāti sarvaṃ svarūpataḥ ||52||
bhedavijñānino mohādvāsate sa na yoginaḥ || 53 ||
vyavahāraḥ svataḥ sarvaḥ svātmanā bhāti kevalam || 54 ||
kalpakoṭiśatenāpi mayā vaktuṃ na śakyate || 55 ||
matto labdhaparijñānāḥ kṛtārthāśva na saṃśayaḥ || 56 ||
bhūyo'pi jñānayajñaṃ tu pravakṣyāmi samāsataḥ ||
itaḥ pūrvaṃ mayā noktamapi kasyacidāstikāḥ || 1 ||
eka eva śivaḥ sākṣātsatyajñānādilakṣaṇaḥ ||
vikārarahitaḥ śuddhaḥ svaśaktyā pañcadhā sthitaḥ ||2||
pañcavidhaṃ tatkṛtyaṃ sṛṣṭisthitisaṃhṛtitirobhāvāḥ |
īśānaśveti tatpūrvapuruṣaśceti suvratāḥ ||
aghoraśveti viprendrā vāmadeva iti dvijāḥ || 3 ||
vāmadevo rasaḥ prokto gandhaḥ sadya udāhṛtaḥ || 5 ||
kramācchabdādibhūtānāṃ devatāśca prakīrtitāḥ || 6 ||
tāśveśānādayaḥ proktāḥ krameṇaiva munīśvarāḥ ||
sarvāṇyetāni viprendrāḥ śiva eva na saṃśayaḥ || 7 ||
ambho vāmastathā bhūmiḥ sadyojātaḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 9 ||
kālāgnirudro vipredrāstathā nārāyaṇābhidhaḥ || 10 ||
brahmā caturmukhaḥ sākṣādākāśādestu devatāḥ ||
etāni śivarūpeṇa paśyanmucyeta bandhanāt || 11 ||
śrotramīśāna eva syāttvakva tatpuruṣaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
cakṣuśvāghora eva syājjihvā vāmaḥ samīritaḥ || 12 ||
pāyuḥ sadya iti proktaḥ sākṣāddedāntapāragaiḥ || 15 ||
mitraśca muniśārdūlāḥ kramātkhānāṃ ca devatāḥ || 16 ||
etāni śivarūpeṇa paśyanmucyeta bandhanāt || 17 ||
śādibhūtapañcakagatarajośaiḥ krameṇāssrabdhatvādīśānādyātmakānītyarthaḥ
mana īśāna eva syādbuddhistatpuruṣaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
ahaṃkārastvaghoraḥ syāścittaṃ vāmaḥ samīritaḥ ||18||
eṣāṃ ca kāraṇaṃ viprā antaḥkaraṇasaṃjñitam ||
sadyojāta iti proktaṃ sarvavedārthapāragaiḥ || 19 ||
cittasya devatā devī śivo'ntaḥkaraṇasya tu || 20 ||
etāni śivarūpeṇa paśyanmucyeta bandhanāt || 21 ||
prāṇa īśāna eva syādapānaḥ puruṣaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
vyāno ghorastathodāno vāmadevaḥ samīritaḥ || 22 ||
samānaḥ sadya eva syātsūtrātmā kāraṇo'nilaḥ ||
viśiṣṭo viśvasṛṣṭiśva viśvayonirajā jayā || 23 ||
krameṇa devatāḥ proktāḥ prāṇādīnāṃ munīśvarāḥ ||
etāni śivarūpeṇa paśyanmucyeta bandhanāt || 24 ||
pṛthivyādiṣu bhūteṣu yo guṇaḥ sattvasaṃjñitaḥ ||
sa krameṇa nivṛttyādikalāsaṃjñāmupaiti ca || 25 ||
śāntyatītakalā caitā vyutkrameṇa munīśvarāḥ ||
bhavanti pañca brahmāṇi tathā bhūteṣu pañcasu || 27 ||
sthito rajoguṇo viprā ākāśādikrameṇa ca ||
spandaścaiva parispandaḥ prakramaḥ pariśīlanaḥ || 28 ||
etāni pañca brahmāṇi bhavanti munisattamāḥ || 29 ||
chādakaṃ bādhakaṃ mugdhaṃ nodakaṃ bhañjakaṃ bhavet || 30 ||
etāni śivarūpeṇa paśyanmucyeta bandhanāt ||31||
tāni ca brāhmaṇāḥ pañca brahmāṇi syurna saṃśayaḥ ||32||
māyayaiva śivaḥ sākṣātpañcadhā samavasthitaḥ ||
sā śivasya sadā māyā sarvadurghaṭakāriṇī || 34 ||
vastutaḥ śaṃbhurānandaḥ satyasaṃpūrṇacidanaḥ ||
māyayā mohitā martyāstaṃ bhedena vidurbudhāḥ || 36 ||
ahaṃ sa iti saṃmohastathā trīṇi parityajet || 37 ||
saṃsārārṇavamagnānāṃ jantūnāmavivekinām ||
agatīnāṃ gatiḥ sākṣājjñānameva hi kevalam || 41 ||
svaśakteḥ śatrubhūtānāṃ rāgādīnāṃ durātmanām ||
chedane vedanaṃ śastraṃ kevalaṃ khalu netarat || 42 ||
saṃsāraduḥkhataptānāmātmajñānāmṛtāmbhasā ||
tāpaśāntirna cānyena satyameva na saṃśayaḥ || 43 ||
bhūmiḥ sṛjati gṛhṇāti yathaṣadhivanaspatīn ||
tathā śaṃbhuridaṃ sarva sṛṣṭvā ca grasate svayam || 47 ||
svayameva yathā svapnaṃ sṛṣṭvā gṛhṇāti cetanaḥ ||
tathā śaṃbhuridaṃ sarva sṛṣṭvā ca grasate svayam || 48 ||
tathaiva svaprapañco'pi svayaṃ syātsvaprabodhataḥ || 49 ||
sa dhīraḥ sa tu sarvajñaḥ sa śivaḥ sa tu durlabhaḥ ||50||
jāyate pūrṇavijñānaṃ keṣāṃcitpuṇyagauravāt ||
tathā'pi prativaddhaṃ syātprasādena vinā kṛtam ||52||
pratibandhavinirmuktaṃ bhavettadvi vimuktidam || 53 ||
śivaśaṃkararudrākhyaḥ sāmbaḥ satyādilakṣaṇaḥ ||
paramātmā hi vijñānaprasādaṃ kurute sadā || 54 ||
jñānaprasādaṃ kurute na viṣṇurna pitāmahaḥ ||
na cendro na ca tigmāṃśurna candro nānyadevatāḥ || 55 ||
viśuddhamanasāṃ nṛṇāṃ viṣṇupūrvāśva devatāḥ ||
yathādhikāraṃ kurvanti praṇāḍyā satyamīritam || 56 ||
kaluṣīkṛtacittānāṃ viṣṇubrahmapurogamāḥ ||
yathādhikāraṃ kurvanti prasādaṃ bhuktisiddhaye || 57 ||
ato jñānaprasādārtha śivaḥ sāmbaḥ sanātanaḥ ||
upāsitavyo mantavyaḥ śrotavyaśca mumukṣubhiḥ ||58||
śivaprasādena vinā na muktayaḥ || 59 ||
viśuddhavijñānadivākaraḥ svayaṃ
pradugdhapāpasya tamovināśakṛt || 60 ||
iti prajātaṃ yadi vedanaṃ nṛṇāṃ
taranti saṃsāramahodadhiṃ te || 61 ||
bhūyo'pi jñānayajñaṃ tu pravakṣyāmi samāsataḥ ||
śṛṇuta śreyase viprāḥ śraddhayā parayā saha || 1 ||
ārabhyate bhūyo'pīti || 1 ||
ghaṭakubyakusūlādipadārtheṣu munīśvarāḥ ||
sā viśeṣeṇa rūpeṇa vibhinneti ca kecana || 2 ||
viśeṣarūpasyābhāvādbhedābhāvena hetunā ||
sati bhede viśeṣaḥ syānnābhede hi munīśvarāḥ || 4 ||
śūnyameva bhavennaiva bhedākāro bhaveddijāḥ || 5 ||
viśeṣārthapratītistu bhrāntisiddhā na saṃśayaḥ ||
sattāyā yadi bhinnaṃ cedbrahmāsatsyānṛśṛṅgavat || 8 ||
sākṣātkāreṇa tadavidyānivṛttau tatkāryasyāpi dṛśyaprapañcasya nivṛttistaṃdā
te tu sattātirekeṇa na vidyante kathaṃcana || 9 ||
brahmaivedamiti prāha śrutirapyatinirmalā || 10 ||
ataḥ sarvamidaṃ śaṃbhuriti vitta vicakṣaṇāḥ || 11 ||
mṛccharāvādirūpeṇa yathā bhāti svabhāvataḥ ||
tathā sarvatayā bhāti śivaḥ sarvāvabhāsakaḥ ||
tathā sarvatayā bhāti śivaḥ sarvāvabhāsakaḥ || 13 ||
śaktikā rajatākārā yathā bhāti svabhāvataḥ |
tathā sarvatayā bhāti śivaḥ sarvāvabhāsakaḥ || 14 ||
pyarajatākāreṇa bhāsate tathā paraśivo'pi svāśritamāyāvaśātsarvajagadātmanā
tathā sarvatayā bhāti śivaḥ sarvāvibhāsakaḥ || 15 ||
andhakāraḥ prakāśaśca yathā''kāśe prakāśate ||
jaḍājaḍamidaṃ sarve tathā bhāti parātmani || 16 ||
mahadādiviśepāntaṃ jagadbhāti tathā''tmani || 17 ||
vanāni śaṃbhurgirayaśva śaṃbhuḥ ||
tataḥ sa ekaḥ paramārthametat || 18 ||
mṛgyaśva devairamarendrapūrvaiḥ || 19 ||
tapobhiruḥ satataṃ viśiṣṭā
namanti nityaṃ vacasā stuvanti || 20 ||
yatīndravṛndā hṛdi saṃniviṣṭaṃ
cidātmarūpaṃ vidurenameva || 21 ||
śivamaśeṣamidaṃ paripaśyataḥ
paramarūpatayaiva vibhāti hi || 22 ||
kathamaśeṣajagatpratibhā bhavet || 23 ||
paramaśivamaśeṣaṃ paśyatāmādibhūtaṃ
na phalanikarabhogaprāptaye tadbhavecca || 24 ||
brahmavitpravarasya tu vaibhavam || 25 ||
dbrahmavedanameva taduttamam || 26 ||
bādarāyaṇo'pi paratatvajñānātsaṃcitā gāmikarmaṇovināśāśleṣau sūtrapāmāsa
sarpādibhāvena vibhāsamānā
śivo na viśvaṃ śiva eva tatsvayam || 27 ||
11 25 11
na baddhamukto na ca baddha eva tu || 29 ||
saṃtasaṃhitā |
kasyacicca na vandhanamocane || 30 ||
iyaṃ hi vedasya parā hi niṣṭhā
munīśvarāṇāmapi śaṃkarasya tu ||
patanti te mohaphaṇīndradaṣṭāḥ || 31 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi jñānotpattestu kāraṇam ||
vinā yena śivajñānaṃ na jāyeta kathaṃcana || 1 ||
devatāḥ sakalā nityaṃ prārthayenmatimattamaḥ || 2 ||
śaṃ na indraśca vāgīśaḥ śaṃ no viṣṇururukramaḥ ||
namo'stu brahmaṇe vāyo namo'stu tava śobhanam || 4 ||
tvameva sākṣādbrahmāsi tvāṃ vadiṣyāmi śaṃkaram ||
ṛtaṃ ca satyaṃ cāhaṃ tvāṃ vadiṣyāmi viśeṣataḥ || 5 ||
māṃ bhūyo'vatu vaktāramapi cāvatu śobhanam || 6 ||
śāntiḥ śāntiḥ punaḥ śāntirdoṣatrayanivṛttaye ||
kṛtvaivaṃ prārthanāmātmajñānārthaṃ punarāstikāḥ || 7 ||
me gopāyetiparyantamaryantaśraddhayā saha || 8 ||
saṃkoco dehayātrāyāṃ yadi jñānārthino bhavet ||
upakṣīṇā bhavedvistatra tasya na saṃśayaḥ || 9 ||
ājyenānnena comābhyāmāvahantīti mantrataḥ || 10 ||
juhuyācchradvayā sārdhaṃ brahmacārī gṛhī vanī ||
bhikṣukastu japemantramanagniḥ śradvayā saha || 11 ||
nityamācāryaśuśrūṣāṃ prakuryādbhaktipūrvakam ||
utthāyotthāya paṭ trīṇi praṇāmaṃ dvādaśātha vā ||12||
vedāntaśravaṇaṃ kuryānmananaṃ ca samāhitaḥ || 13 ||
śānto dānto bhavennityaṃ virakto bhikṣuko bhavet || 14 ||
śītoṣṇasukhaduḥkheṣu tathā mānāpamānayoḥ ||
sahiṣṇuśca bhavennityaṃ tathaikāgramanā bhavet || 15 ||
rudrākṣadhāraṇaṃ kuryādro rudrākṣadhāraṇāt ||
pratibandhaka bāhulyālajjā nityaṃ prajāyate || 16 ||
adṛśyadarśanādau ca japetprājñaḥ paḍakṣaram || 17 ||
saṃbhāṣaṇādikaṃ tena kuryādevāvicārataḥ || 18 ||
saṃbhāṣaṇādikaṃ nīcairna kuryānmohato'pi vā ||
yadi kuryātpramādena prāyaśvittī bhaveddijaḥ || 19 ||
viśiṣṭā api nīcāḥ syurna saṃbhāṣyā dvijottamaiḥ||20||
- sūtasaṃhitā |
agnirityādibhirmantrejībālokteśva saptabhiḥ || 21 ||
bhasmanā tena sarvānaṃ samuḍūlya tataḥ param || 22 ||
lalāṭe ca tathā skaṃdhe tathaivorasi dhārayet || 23 ||
pratimāsaṃ viśeṣeṇa sevanīyāni bhaktitaḥ || 24 ||
utsavaṃ sevamānasya muktirhastasthitā bhavet || 25 ||
gurūcchiṣṭaṃ puroḍāśaṃ bhavatyeva na saṃśayaḥ ||
nirmālyaṃ ca nivedyaṃ ca bhuktvā cāndrāyaṇaṃ caret ||28||
varṇāśramādihīnānāṃ kuryātsevāṃ na mānavaḥ ||
saha vāsaṃ na taiḥ kuryātsaha saṃbhāṣaṇaṃ tathā || 29 ||
sahaiva gamanaṃ sakhyaṃ saha saṃbandhameva ca || 30 ||
devānāṃ ca manuṣyāṇāṃ tathā'nyeṣāṃ ca lāñchanam ||
na kuryānmohato vā'pi yadi kuryātpatatyadhaḥ ||31||
śrautasmārtasadācāre nādhikārī ca lāñchitaḥ ||32||
lāñchitāśca na saṃbhāṣyā na spṛśyāśca tathaiva ca ||
na darśanīyāstānrājā deśācchīghraṃ pravāsayet || 33 ||
devāñca pitryātkāryācca mātāpitrādipūjanāt ||
tathā'nyebhyaśca karmabhyaḥ śrautebhyaśca tathaiva ca || 36 ||
uktasādhanasaṃpanno jñānādbhasmādhigacchati || 37 ||
anupraviṣṭaṃ tadrūpaṃ bhasmaleśamudāhṛtam ||
tena lepena deveśaḥ prativimvena bhasmanā || 39 ||
sa eva pūjanīyastu brahmaviṣṇumurottamaiḥ || 40 ||
taṃ viditvā vimucyante śāntā dāntā yatīśvarāḥ ||
gṛhasthāśva tathaivānye satyadharmaparāyaṇāḥ || 42 ||
bhasmasaṃchannasarvāṅgāstripuṇḍrāṅkitamastakāḥ ||
rudrākṣamālābharaṇāḥ śrīmatpañcākṣarapriyāḥ || 43 ||
ato jñānārthibhirjñānasādhanāni manīṣibhiḥ || 44 ||
saṃpādyāni mahāyāsājjñānānmucyeta bandhanāva ||
jñānaṃ vedāntavijñānaṃ brahmātmaikatvagocaram || 45 ||
gurūpadiṣṭo vedārthaḥ saṃgraheṇa mayoditaḥ ||
maduktārthe tu viśvāsaṃ kurudhvaṃ yatnato dvijāḥ || 50 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi vairāgyaṃ duḥkhanāśanam ||
yena sākṣācchivajñānaṃ jāyate mokṣasādhanam || 1 ||
ājñayā devadevasya kālapākena karmaṇām ||
śobhanāśobhanabhrāntiḥ kalpitā paramārthavat || 3 ||
icchā nityaṃ prajāyeta narāṇāṃ mūḍhacetasām || 4||
śobhanatvena saṃkḷptaḥ padārthoṃ dvividhaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
eka aihika ākhyāta itaraḥ pāralaukikaḥ || 5 ||
punarbhukteṣu cārtheṣu tatsamāneṣu mānavaḥ || 6 ||
śobhanakhena yaḥ klṛptaḥ padārthaḥ pāralaukikaḥ || 7 ||
tatra vṛddhiṃ nṛṇāṃ śāstramutpādayati niścitam ||
śramāttagogavāñchā ca jāyate sarvadehinām || 8 ||
dṛṣṭānuśrāvikadvārā vṛddhisaṃtatirātmanaḥ ||
kalpite viṣaye nityaṃ jāyate vedavittamāḥ || 9 ||
rāgadvepārgalāvā dharmādharmavaśaṃgatāḥ ||
devatiryaṅmanuṣyādinirayaṃ yānti mānavāḥ ||
rāgadvepāvevālā tasyāṃ baddhāḥ puṇyapāpātmakakarmapāravaśyaṃ gatāḥ sarve
śukraṃ ca śoṇitaṃ dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā smṛtvā tu mānavaḥ ||
udvāraṃ kurute tadvi śarīraṃ cetanasya tu || 12 ||
tasmiñśarīre'haṃnuddhiṃ sadā kaḥ kurute janaḥ ||
mūḍho'haṃ mamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti vigraham || 13 ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā carma bhūmitale sthitam ||
udgāraṃ kurute martyaḥ svayaṃ taddopadarśanāt || 14 ||
tasmivarmaṇyahaṃ buddhiṃ sadā kaḥ kurute naraḥ || 15 ||
mūḍho'haṃmamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam ||
dṛṣṭvā sṣṭaṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā māṃsaṃ bhūmitale sthitam || 16 ||
tathaivā''tmatayā'grāhye dehe māṃsaṃ tu yadbhavet || 17 ||
mūḍho'haṃmamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam || 18 ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā śiṃrāṃ bhūmitale sthitām ||
udgāraṃ kurute martyaḥ svayaṃ taddopadarśanāt || 19 ||
tathaivā''tmatayā'grāhyā śarīrasthā ca yā śirā ||
tasyāmeva tvabuddhiṃ sadā kaḥ kurute janaḥ || 20 ||
mūḍho'haṃmamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam ||
dṛṣṭvā sṣṭaṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā cāsthi bhūmitale sthitam ||21||
tathaivā''tmatayā'grāhyaṃ śarīrasyāsthi yadbhavet ||22||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā romapuñjaṃ bhuvi sthitam ||
udgāraṃ kurute martyaḥ svayaṃ tadopadarśanāt || 24 ||
tasminneva khabuddhiṃ sadā kaḥ kurute janaḥ || 25 ||
mūḍho'haṃmamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā raktaṃ bhūmitale sthitam || 26 ||
tathaivāSStmatayā'grāhyaṃ raktaṃ yaddehasaṃsthitam || 27 ||
mūḍho'haṃmamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam || 28 ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā pūyaṃ bhūmitale sthitam ||
tasminneva tvabuddhiṃ sadā kaḥ kurute janaḥ || 30 ||
mūḍho'haṃ mamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā ślepmarāśiṃ bhuvi sthitam || 31 ||
tathaiva puramadhyasthe śleṣmarāśo vicakṣaṇaḥ || 32 ||
kaḥ karoti khabuddhiṃ manuṣyaḥ paṇḍitottamāḥ ||
mūḍho'haṃmamabuddhibhyāmidaṃ gṛhṇāti saṃtatam || 33 ||
dṛṣṭvā sṣṭaṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā pittaṃ bhūmitale sthitam ||
udgāraṃ kurute martyaḥ svayaṃ taddoṣadarśanāt || 34 ||
kaḥ karoti tvahaṃbuddhiṃ mūḍha evaṃ karoti hi || 35 ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā mūtraṃ bhūmitale sthitam ||
udgāraṃ kurute martyaḥ svayaṃ taddoṣadarśanāt || 36 ||
kaḥ karoti tvahaṃbuddhiṃ mūḍha eva karoti hi || 37 ||
dṛṣṭvā spṛṣṭvā tathā smṛtvā purīṣaṃ bhūtale sthitam ||
udgāraṃ kurute martyaḥ svayaṃ taddopadarśanāt || 38 ||
bhakṣyabhojyādayaḥ sarve padārthāśvātiśobhanāḥ ||
malaṃ bhavanti yatsparśāttatkathaṃ śobhanaṃ vapuḥ || 41 ||
tatkathaṃ śobhanaṃ piṇḍaṃ bhavedvata dvijottamāḥ || 42 ||
atīva dhavalāḥ śuddhāḥ paṭā yatsaṃgamena tu ||
bhavanti malinā varṣma kathaṃ tacchobhanaṃ bhavet || 43 ||
krimikośamidaṃ varṣma duḥkhāya na sukhāya hi ||44||
jaṭhare vāyusaṃcāracūrṇite garbhatāṃ gataḥ ||
duḥkhameva tadā tasya sukhaṃ kiṃcinna vidyate || 48 ||
purīṣamūtrasaṃpūrṇe jaṭhare garbhatāṃ gataḥ ||
duḥkhameva sadā yāti na kiṃcitsukhamāpnuyāt || 49 ||
vālye pīḍā mahātītrā gaṇapīḍā mahattarā ||
pipīlikādipīḍā ca parihartuṃ na śakyate || 53 ||
vyādhipīḍā mahātītrā kṣutpīḍā ca dine dine ||
pipāsā ca mahāpīḍā kathaṃ yoti sukhaṃ naraḥ || 54 ||
akṣaragrahaṇe pīḍā pīḍā ca paṭhane tathā ||
śabdajālasya duḥkhābdherna pāro dṛśyate mayā || 55 ||
śrautasmārtasadācāre mahāpīḍā ca dāruṇā ||
niṣiddhaparihāre ca kathaṃ yāti sukhaṃ naraḥ || 56 ||
strībhogātmakatā duḥkhaṃ duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 57 ||
strīṇāmārādhane duḥkhaṃ tāsāṃ saṃrakṣaṇe'pi ca ||
tāsāṃ paribhave duḥkhaṃ duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 58 ||
vastrasaṃpādane duḥkhaṃ bhūṣaṇānāṃ tathaiva ca ||
rakṣaṇe ca tathā teṣāṃ duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 59 ||
gṛhakṣetra dhanādīnāṃ duḥkhaṃ saṃpādane tathā ||
rakṣaṇe ca tathā duḥkhaṃ teṣāmeva vicārataḥ || 60 ||
janmanāśabhayāduḥkhaṃ duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 61 ||
dāsabhāve mahaduḥkhaṃ duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 62 ||
mārgetkarṣaparijñāne duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 63 ||
sūtasaṃhitāṃ |
paraiḥ sāmye mahaduḥkhaṃ duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 64 ||
vāyupīḍā'gnipīḍā ca toyapīḍā tathaiva ca ||
sarpādidaṃśane pīḍā duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 65 ||
bhūtapretapiśācānāṃ yakṣādīnāṃ tathaiva ca ||
viṣṇuloke ca raudre ca duḥkhameva vicārataḥ || 67 ||
duḥkhaṃ duḥkhātmanā kiṃcijjānāti vivaśaḥ pumān ||
sukhātmanā ca jānāti bhramāduḥkhaṃ kadācana || 69 ||
pañcalipsā puruṣaspa kuta ityata āha- tadajñānavaleneti || 70 ||
tātparya dīpikāsametā
jahāti duḥkhamaprāptaṃ svataḥ satyaṃ mayoditam || 71 ||
ajñānasya nivṛttiśva jñānādeva na karmaṇā ||
jñānaṃ nāma mahādevajñānaṃ vedāntavākyajam ||
viraktasya hi saṃsārājjñānaṃ nānyasya kasyacit ||72||
taniṣkampadīpasadṛśenaikāgryeṇa manasā sūkṣmatattvaṃ sākṣātkiyate nānyasya
tadā maryo'mṛto bhavatyatra brahma samaśrute || 73 ||
anātmanāmanityatvaṃ ghaṭādīnāṃ jaḍātmanām ||
āvālapaṇḍitaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ yato'taḥ paṇḍitottamāḥ || 2 ||
na tadyuktamakāryasyāpyanityatvaprasiddhitaḥ || 3 ||
akāryasya ghaṭādīnāṃ prāgabhāvasya jantubhiḥ ||
dṛṣṭameva nityatvaṃ nādṛṣṭaṃ paṇḍitottamāḥ || 4 ||
śrutyanugrāhakastarko na svatantra iti sthitiḥ || 7 ||
dṛṣṭasāmyena vedajñāḥ khalu tarko'rthasādhakaḥ ||
śrutiranyānapekṣā hi dvijendrā arthasādhikā || 8||
pratyakṣādipramāṇānāṃ pañcānāṃ paṇḍitottamāḥ ||
jagamyaṃ brahma dharmaścādharmaḥ śrutyaiva gamyate || 9 ||
te kareṇāpi mādhurya jānantyeva suniśvitam || 10 ||
antareṇeti || 10 ||
purā kaśvinmahāmūrkhaḥ saṃgiro nāma vāḍavaḥ ||
pūrvajanmakṛtātpāpāddedaśraddhāvivarjitaḥ || 11 ||
dharmādharmau ca tarkeṇa kevalena munīśvarāḥ || 12 ||
tarkoṃ nānāvidhastasya pratibhāto munīśvarāḥ || 13 ||
tena mohāvṛtaḥ sadyaḥ saṃgiro munipuṅgavāḥ ||
cakāra dīkṣāṃ pāṣaṇḍamārge śraddhāpuraḥsaram || 14 ||
