cakāra dīkṣāṃ pāpaṇḍaviśeṣeṣu yathāruci || 15 ||
punastarkāpratiṣṭhānānmāyayā parimohitaḥ ||
tyaktvā pāṣaṇḍamārge ca cacāra ca yathāruci ||16||
16. pākhaṇḍamārge |
punarmohāvṛtaḥ sākṣātsvasāraṃ mātaraṃ tathā ||
gatvā mamāra kālena saṃgiraḥ sohaṃsī dvijaḥ || 17 ||
saṃgiraṃ tu samādāya śīghraṃ viprā yamaṃ yayuḥ || 18 ||
yathāśakti bhaṭā eṣa pīḍyatāṃ mama saṃnidhau || 19 ||
atīva pīḍito viprā abhavañca viceṣṭitaḥ || 20 ||
punaśca tīkṣṇayā vācā yamaḥ prāha sudāruṇam ||
bhidyatāṃ saṃgiro duṣṭaśchidyatāṃ dahyatāmayam || 21 ||
ikṣuyantrādiṣu pa pīḍyatāmaniśaṃ bhaṭāḥ ||
yantrairnānāvidhairanyairupāyairatidāruṇaiḥ || 23 ||
purākṛta mahāpuṇya paripākabalena ca || 24 ||
akasmādāgatastatra mahātejā mahāmatiḥ || 25 ||
śaṃbhubhaktaḥ śatānando nāmrā śaṃbhurivāparaḥ |
sa punaḥ pīḍyamānaṃ taṃ vilokya karuṇāvalāt ||26||
prāhoṃnamaḥ śivāyeti mantrarājaṃ paḍakṣaram ||
tadaiva narakaḥ sākṣātsvargaloko'bhavadvijāḥ || 27 ||
18.2 imādvijaḥ |
puṣpavṛṣṭirabhavatsumaṅgalāṃ
cakuragnivimalā vicakṣaṇāḥ || 28 ||
yakṣakiṃnarapuraḥsarā bhṛśaṃ
nṛttagītasukhabhogino'bhavan || 29 ||
śriyā ca viṣṇuḥ saha modasaṃyutaḥ || 30 ||
yamo'tibhītaḥ parameśvarājñayā
pravartamānaśca kṛtāñjalirdvijāḥ ||
bahupraṇāmaṃ śivaśaṅkayā'karot || 31 ||
vimuñca bhītiṃ yama śaṃkarājñayā
pravartamāneti vacaḥ sukhāvaham || 32 ||
