nirbhayaśva tarasā'bhavadyamaḥ || 33 ||
idaṃ babhāṣe vacanaṃ sukhāvahaṃ
samasta lokasya munīśvareśvaraḥ || 34 ||
śivarudrādiśabda yo viśiṣṭaṃ veda mānavaḥ ||
umayā sahitāṃ śuddhāṃ trinetrāṃ candraśekharām ||
parasya mūrti yo veda taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 37 ||
yo vedāSStmatayā nityaṃ taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 38 ||
yo dadhāti mahāprītyā taṃ khaṃ parihara prabhum || 39 ||
yaḥ karoti svakaṃ dehaṃ taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 40 ||
nityaṃ line mahādevaṃ sākṣātsaṃsāramocakam ||
ārādhayati yo martyastaṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 41 ||
rudrākṣaṃ trīṇi ṣaṃḍekaṃ parayā śradvayā saha ||
dadhāti nityaṃ yo martyastaṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 42||
śāntidāntyādisaṃyuktaḥ śaṃkare bhaktisaṃyutaḥ ||
yaḥ sarvakarmasaṃnyāsī taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 43 ||
yaḥ karoti mahāprītyā taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 44 ||
vedavedāntaniṣṭhasya guroḥ śuśrūṣaṇe rataḥ ||
yaḥ karotīha śuśrūṣāṃ taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 45 ||
yo rudra yajate prītyā taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhum || 46 ||
yaḥ karoti mahāprītyā taṃ tvaṃ parihara prabhubhū || 47 ||
yo na vākke sadā prītyā taṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam ||48||
mahādevasamaṃ viṣṇuṃ brahmāṇaṃ cānyameva vā ||
manute yaḥ svamohena taṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam || 49 ||
yo nā''carati mohena taṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam ||50||
mānuṣaṃ daivikaṃ cānyatsvaśarīre'ṅkanaṃ naraḥ ||
yaḥ karoti bhramāddā'pi taṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam ||51||
ūrdhvapuṇḍraṃ triśūlaṃ vā vartulaṃ yastu vaidikaḥ ||
dadhāti mohato vā'pi taṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam ||52||
aśrautācārasaṃpannaḥ śrotācāraparāṅmukhaḥ ||
gurudrohī ca yo matyaistaṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam || 53 ||
vedādanyasya cotkarṣe taṃ tvaṃ ghātaya durjanam || 54 ||
evamuktvā muniḥ śrīmāñśatānandasamāhvayaḥ ||
kailāsamagamadrudraṃ tatra stotuṃ kutūhalāt || 55 ||
yamo 'pi saṃgiraṃ viprāḥ samāhūyā''dureṇa ca ||
vinaiva vedaṃ tarkasya kevalasya parigrahāt || 56 ||
purākṛtena puṇyena mahādevaprasādataḥ || 57 ||
duḥkhādapi vinirmuktastvaṃ mahātmansukhapradam || 58 ||
taduktaṃ dharmamāsthāya punarvedāntavākyam || 59 ||
ityuktvā''śu yamaḥ śrīmānagamatsvapuraṃ prati || 60 ||
tarkasiddho'tiduḥstho'rthaḥ pratyavāyasya kāraṇam ||6||
rauravādipu saṃtaptā abhavanvedavittamāḥ || 62 ||
spṛṣṭisteṣāṃ narāṇāṃ tu narakāya na saṃśayaḥ || 63 ||
