ghaṭapaṭā |
pratyaye tu cidākāro vṛttyākāraśca suvratāḥ ||
vidyate mohamāhātmyādekākārāvabhāsanam || 5 ||
bhāvāṃśaḥ karaṇāṃśaśca vidyate pratyaye'pi ca ||
bhāvāṃśastu cidākāro vṛttyaṃśaḥ karaṇāṃśakaḥ || 6 ||
vṛttināśena vṛttisthaṃ cidākāraṃ munīśvarāḥ || 10 ||
evaṃ śramavaśādeva bhāvāṃśakaraṇāṃśayorvivekāparijñānātkaraṇāṃśavṛttināśe
jñātājñātārthajātasya yaḥ sākṣī bhāsate svayam ||
sa eva sākṣāñcinmātrasvabhāvātmā na cāparaḥ || 12 ||
vināṃśe sākṣiṇo nāśastathā naiva bhaviṣyati ||
sattākāle tu sattvācca vināśaḥ mutarāṃ na hi ||14||
janmanāśapratītistu nāntareṇaiva sākṣiṇam ||
janmanāśau muniśreṣṭhāḥ svata eva na sidhyataḥ ||15||
sākṣiṇo janmanāśau tu na cānyenaiva sidhyataḥ || 16 ||
sākṣirūpeṇa cānyena janmanāśau na sidhyataḥ ||
abhāvādeva cānyasya sākṣirūpasya suvratāḥ || 17 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
sākṣyākāreṇa caikatvātsākṣibhedo na sidhyati || 18 ||
sākṣyarūpeṇa bhedastu sākṣyasyaiva na sākṣiṇaḥ ||
sākṣimātratayā bhedābhāve'pyasyaiva sākṣiṇaḥ || 19 ||
te mahāmohasarpeṇa daṣṭā eva na saṃśayaḥ || 20 ||
viśeṣarūpaṃ cidvapaṃ jaḍarūpaṃ tuṃ vā bhavet ||
na rūpāntarameva syāttādṛśasyānirūpaṇāt || 21 ||
cidrūpaṃ sākṣimātraṃ syānna cānyatparamārthataḥ ||
jaḍarūpaṃ ca nāstyeva sākṣiṇaḥ paramārthataḥ || 22 ||
prakāśasya tamo rūpaṃ yathā loke na sidhyati || 23 ||
ato viśeṣākāreṇa bhedaṃ ye sarvasākṣiṇaḥ ||
vadanti te mahābhrāntā nimagnāśca bhavārṇave || 24 ||
brahmatvaṃ ca dvijā vedā vadanti śraddhayā saha || 25 ||
nityatvaṃ śuddhabuddhatvamātmanaḥ pravadanti hi || 27 ||
jihvāyāṃ paraśuṃ taptaṃ dhārayāmi na saṃśayaḥ || 28 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi viśiṣṭaṃ dharmamādarāva ||
śṛṇutātyantakalyāṇaṃ munayaḥ parayāṃ mudā || 1 ||
purā vedavidāṃ mukhyāḥ kāvaṣeyā maharṣayaḥ ||
satrāvasāne saṃbhūya śraddhayā parayā saha || 2 ||
vicārya suciraṃ kālaṃ viśiṣṭaṃ dharmamāstikāḥ ||
punaḥ saṃśayamāpannā viṣaṇṇā vivaśāśva te || 3 ||
gatvā himavataḥ pārśve trikālasrānasaṃyutāḥ ||
bhasmoddhūlitasarvāṅgāstripuṇḍrāṅkitamastakāḥ || 4 ||
śaktipāṇirmahātejā dvitīya iva śaṃkaraḥ ||
skandaḥ sarvajagatsvāmī pratyakṣamabhavatsvayam || 7 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā munayaḥ sarve prasanendriyamānasāḥ ||
bhaktyā paramayā yuktā vivaśā gadakharāḥ || 8 ||
praṇamya daṇḍavaḍūmāvutthāyotthāya sādaram ||
stotraiḥ stutvā mahātmānaṃ samabhyarcya yathāvalam || 9 ||
so'pi sarvajagatsvāmī tārakārirmahādyutiḥ || 10 ||
sarvavijñānaratnānāmākaraḥ karuṇākaraḥ ||
suprasannaḥ svayaṃ prāha munīnāṃ dharmamuttamam || 11 ||
śṛṇudhvaṃ munayaḥ sarve mahābhāgyasamanvitāḥ ||
vadāmi saṃgraheṇāhaṃ yuṣmākaṃ dharmamuttamam || 12 ||
dharmācchreṣṭhaḥ samākhyātaḥ samūlo dharma āstikāḥ||15||
dharmaḥ śreṣṭha iti prokto mayā vedārthapāragāḥ || 16 ||
dharmaḥ śreṣṭha iti prokto dharmatattvaviśāradaiḥ || 17 ||
dharmaḥ śreṣṭha iti proktaḥ sarvadharmārthavedibhiḥ || 18 ||
prājāpatyāgamaproktādvarmāddedavidāṃ varāḥ ||
mayā śreṣṭha iti proko dharmo viṣṇvāgamoditaḥ ||19||
viṣṇvāgamoditādvarmādaśeṣādāstikottamāḥ
śaivāgamodito dharmo dvidhā pūrvamudīritaḥ || 20 ||
adhaḥsrotodbhavastveka ūrdhvasrotovo'paraḥ || 21 ||
kāmikādiprabhedena sa bhinno'nekadhā dvijāḥ || 22 ||
smārtabhyaḥ śrautadharmāśca variṣṭhā munisattamāḥ ||
teṣāṃ śāntyādayaḥ śreṣṭhāstepāṃ bhasmāvaguṇṭhanam || 24 ||
rudrākṣadhāraṇaṃ cāpi śivādyākhyābhibhāṣaṇam ||
śivaliṅgārcanaṃ bhaktyā śivo'hamiti bhāvanā || 25 ||
śivajñānaikaniṣṭasya śuśrūṣā ca viśiṣyate ||
teṣāṃ vedāntavākyānāṃ tātparyasya nirūpaṇam || 26 ||
bhasmasādhananiṣṭhānāṃ sākṣādbhasma śivābhidham ||
prakāśate yathā śāntyā śāntaṃ vastu parātparam ||29||
vedavākyasamutpannaṃ śivajñānaṃ nirūpaṇe ||
samyagjñānaṃ mayā''khyātamitaravyavahārataḥ || 31 ||
codanālakṣaṇo dharmo dharmaḥ sākṣānnirūpaṇe ||
itaro vyavahāre tu dharma ityabhiśabdyate || 32 ||
āstikyānvayamātreṇa dharmābhāse'pi suvratāḥ ||
prayukto dharmaśabdastu mukhyo dharmastu vedajaḥ || 33 ||
yathā śaṃbhumo devo nāsti puṇyavatāṃ varāḥ ||
tathā vedasamaṃ mānaṃ nāsti tatra na saṃśayaḥ || 34 ||
ityādinā || 34 ||
tathā vedasamaṃ mānaṃ nāsti tatra na saṃśayaḥ || 35 ||
