evamuktvā munīndrebhyaḥ śrīmānbarhiṇavāhanaḥ ||
jagatsvāmī mahātejāstatraivāntarhito'bhavat || 43 ||
kāvaṣeyā api śreṣṭhāḥ prasādāttārakāriṇaḥ ||
mahādevaṃ mahātmānaṃ dadṛśuḥ svayamāgatam || 44 ||
śrīmatpañcākṣareṇaiva pūjayāmāsurādarāva || 45 ||
munibhyaḥ kāvapeyebhyaḥ svātmajñānaṃ dadau mudā || 46||
• munīndrā api te sarve viśuddhajñānināṃ varāḥ ||
praṇamya devamīśānaṃ sāmvaṃ saṃsārabhepajam || 47 ||
prasādayitvā deveśaṃ kṛtārthā ātmavedanāva ||
niḥspṛhāḥ svātmano'nyatra yayurhimavato gṛham ||48||
viśiṣṭadharmaḥ kathitaḥ samāsatoṃ
dṛthā na lābhāya viśudvacetasām || 49 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi muktisādhanamāstikāḥ ||
śṛṇuta śraddhayā sārdhaṃ sākṣāddedāntadarśitam || 1 ||
• saṃkhyā ca śatameteṣāṃ saha dvādaśasaṃkhyayā || 2 ||
ta ete bhasmadigdhāṅgāstripuṇḍrāṅkitamastakāḥ ||
rudrākṣamālābharaṇā rudrārādhanatatparāḥ || 3 ||
śrīmaddakṣiṇa kailāse sākṣātsaṃsāranāśake || 4 ||
yasminnivasatāṃ nṛṇāmaśeṣāṇāṃ maheśvaraḥ ||
sākṣācchivajñānaniṣṭhasyātipriyeṇa tu ||
bhojanaṃ ca tathā vastraṃ dattvā mucyeta bandhanāt || 9 ||
brāhmaṇānāṃ tathā'nyeṣāmanantaṃ bhavati dhruvam || 10||
tapasā śaṃkarasteṣāṃ prasannaḥ karuṇānidhiḥ ||
sāṃnidhyamakarottatra śaktyā paramayā saha || 11 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sāmvamīśānaṃ sākṣātsaṃsārameṣajam ||
: praṇamya daṇḍavamau papracchurmuktisādhanam || 12 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
varṇāśramasamācārādeva muktirna cānyataḥ || 14 ||
dārānāhṛtya yajñaṃ ca dānaṃ ca vividhaṃ tathā ||
tapaśva vividhaṃ ghoraṃ kṛtvā kāmanayā vinā || 17 ||
pranaṣṭapāpaḥ śudvāntaḥkaraṇo jñānavāñchayā |
viraktaḥ sarvalokebhyo doṣāṇāṃ tu nirūpaṇāt || 18 ||
tatrāmumukṣuḥ saṃnyāsī preritaḥ parameśvarāt || 19 ||
kuṭīcakābhiyāṃ vṛttiṃ vṛttiṃ vā'tha bahūdakām ||
haṃsavṛttiṃ tu vā nityaṃ vāñchate munisattamāḥ || 20 ||
mumukṣurbhikṣuko nityaṃ parahaṃsābhidhāṃ śubhām ||
vṛttimicchati deveśaprasādena dvijottamāḥ || 21 ||
sarveṣāmeva bhikṣūṇāṃ śāntirdāntistitikṣutā ||
srānaṃ śaucamahiṃsā ca mithyābhāṣaṇavarjanam || 23 ||
tripuṇḍradhāraṇaṃ sākṣādbrahmaviṣṇuśivātmakam || 24 ||
sākṣāddedāntavākyānāṃ śravaṇaṃ mananaṃ tathā || 25 ||
parahaṃsasya dharmo'yaṃ viśeṣeṇa samīritaḥ || 26 ||
pūrvapuṇyavalātsākṣātprasādācca śivasya tu ||
brahmātmaviṣayaṃ jñānaṃ labhate bhikṣuko'cirāt || 27 ||
jñānāddedāntavākyotthānmuktiṃ bhikṣuravāpnuyāt ||
vinā jñānena muktistu na sidhyati na sidhyati || 28||
muktisādhanamākhyātaṃ saṃgraheṇa munīśvarāḥ ||
jñāne. yūyamapi śraddhāṃ kurudhvaṃ yatnataḥ sadā || 29 ||
ityuktvā bhagavānsdraḥ sākṣātsaṃsāramocakaḥ ||
jāgamāntakasaṃvedyastatraivāntarhito'bhavat || 30 ||
matto labdhaparijñānā abhavannacireṇa tu || 31 ||
vāñchitārthapradaṃ nṛṇāmiti vitta vicakṣaṇāḥ || 32 ||
śrīmaddakṣiṇakelāsamadṛṣṭvā muktimicchataḥ ||
nāsti saṃsāravicchittiḥ satyaṃ satyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||33||
varṇāśramasamācāraṃ vinā kaivalyamicchataḥ ||
nāsti kaivalyasaṃsiddhiḥ satyaṃ satyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||34||
14. *19*1
viṣṇuprajāpatīndrebhyaḥ śivasyā''dhikyamādarāt ||
nāsti kaivalyamityeṣā śāśvatī śrutirāha hi || 36 ||
bhagavānapi sarvajñaḥ śivaḥ kāruṇikottamaḥ ||
vinā vedāntavijñānaṃ na muktiriti cā''ha hi || 37||
vinā jñānaṃ na kaivalyamityāhurvedā vettamāḥ || 38 ||
vinā jñānaṃ na kaivalyamityāhurvedavittamāḥ || 39 ||
muktisādhanavijñānaṃ vedādeva na cānyataḥ || 40 ||
anyamārgajanitaṃ vicārato vedamārgarucikāraṇaṃ kramāt || 41 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi mārgaprāmāṇyanirṇayam ||
śraddhayā sahitā yūyaṃ śṛṇudhvaṃ munipuṅgavāḥ || 1 ||
vedāṃśca dharmaśāstrāṇi purāṇaṃ bhārataṃ tathā ||
vedāṅgānyupavedāṃśva kāmikādyāgamānapi || 2 ||
kāpālaṃ lākulaṃ caiva tayorbhedāndijarṣabhāḥ ||
teṣāmevopabhedāṃśca śataśo'tha sahasraśaḥ ||
viṣṇvāgamāṃstathā brāhmānbudvādyāgamānapi || 4 ||
mīmāṃsāmatigambhīrāṃ sāṃkhyayogau tathaiva ca || 5 ||
nirmame śaṃkaraḥ sākṣātsarvajñaḥ saṃgraheṇa tu || 6||
siddhavidyādharā yakṣā rākṣasādyāstathaiva ca || 7 ||
munayaśca manuṣyāśca yathābhāgyaṃ dvijottamāḥ ||
tānyeva vistareṇaiva saṃgraheṇaiva vā punaḥ || 8 ||
tarkerete hi mārgāstu na hantavyā manīṣibhiḥ || 9 ||
yathā toyapravāhāṇāṃ samudraḥ paramāvadhiḥ ||
tathaiva sarvamārgāṇāṃ sākṣānniṣṭā maheśvaraḥ || 10 ||
vedamārgasthito devaḥ sākṣānmuktestu kāraṇam || 13 ||
ekarūpā parā muktistatastaddipayā matiḥ || 15 ||
vedāntaḥ śaṃkaraṃ sākṣānnirviśepāhayātmanā || 16 ||
ato mārgāntarājātā matayo munisattamāḥ ||
avidyā naiva vidyāḥ syuriti samyanirūpaṇam ||17||
ato vedāntabhāgastho mahādevo'cireṇa tu || 19 ||
dadāti paramāṃ muktimityepā śāśvatī śrutiḥ || 20 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
jagataḥ kāraṇe muktau jñānādau ca tathaiva ca || 23 ||
mārgāṇāṃ ye viruddhāṃśā vedāntena vicakṣaṇāḥ ||
te'pi mandamatīnāṃ ca mahāmohāvṛtātmanām ||
vāñchāmātrānuguṇyena pravṛttā na yathārthataḥ || 24 ||
darśayitvā tathā kṣudramiṣṭaṃ pūrva maheśvaraḥ ||
paścātpākānuguṇyena dadāti jñānamuttamam || 26 ||
tathā'pi vedo mārgāṇāmuttamaḥ sarvasādhakaḥ || 28 ||
evaṃ buddhvā śrutau śraddhāṃ kurudhvaṃ yatnato dvijāḥ ||29||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi prasādakramamādarāt ||
yasya vijñānamātreṇa prasādaḥ śāṃkaro bhavet || 1 ||
brahmāṇaṃ brahmasaṃpannamapṛcchadidamādarāt || 2 ||
nārāyaṇamanādyantamaṣṭacchadidamuttamam || 3 ||
so'pi nārāyaṇaḥ śrīmānsaha tābhyāmumāpatim ||
kailāsaśikhare ramye samāsīnamatiprabhum || 4 ||
apṛcchaddevadeveśamidaṃ paramakāraṇam || 5 ||
prāha gambhīrayā vācā viṣṇave munipuṅgavāḥ || 6 ||
tacchrutvā bhagavānvyāsaḥ sākṣātpratyakṣaśaṃkarāva |
sanatkumārātsarvajñāduktavānmama sādaram || 7 ||
ahaṃ bhāgyavatāmadya yuṣmākaṃ munipuṅgavāḥ ||
kevalaṃ kṛpayā vakṣye tadeva parayā mudā || 8 ||
nityakarmādyanuṣṭhānātpāpanāśo bhavatyataḥ ||
cittaśuddhirbhavejanto rudrasyaiva prasādataḥ || 9 ||
tato viraktiḥ saṃsārātpunastyāgaśca karmaṇām || 10 ||
punaḥ sāṃkhyābhidhaṃ jñānaṃ pārvatyāstu prasādataḥ ||
sāṃkhyasyotpattivelāyāṃ mocakasya śivasya tu || 13 ||
saṃsāramocakaḥ sākṣācchiva eva na cāparaḥ || 14 ||
anyāśva devatāḥ sarvāḥ praṇāyaiva hi mocakāḥ ||
anekajanmasaṃsiddhaḥ śrautasmārtaparāyaṇaḥ || 15 ||
prāyādapramādena mumukṣuriti hi śrutiḥ || 16 ||
rudrārādhanamevoktaṃ variṣṭamiti vaidikaiḥ || 18 ||
oṃkārasya prasādena viṣṇoścaiva prasādataḥ ||
rudvārādhanavāñchā syāttadārādhanataḥ punaḥ || 19 ||
prasādādeva rudrasya jñānaṃ mokṣaikasādhanam || 20 ||
devayānābhidhā viṣṇorgatiḥ sraṣṭuḥ prasādataḥ ||
brāhmaṇyaṃ kīrtirindośva kherārogyameva tu || 21 ||
puraṃdarasya saubhāgyaṃ valaṃ vāyoḥ prasādataḥ || 22 ||
paṇmukhasya prasādena sarvasiddhirayatnataḥ || 23 ||
śrīdevyāstu prasādena sarvaiśvaryamayatnataḥ || 24 ||
kāmanārahitānāṃ tu śuddhidvāreṇa devatāḥ ||
mahādevaprasādasya hetubhūtā bhavanti hi || 26 ||
svayaṃ muktikaraḥ sākṣātkāmanārahitasya tuṃ ||
cireṇaiva tu kālena śivasyaiva prasādataḥ || 28 ||
mahādevaprasādena samaḥ kaśvinna vidyate || 29 ||
brahmendrādipadaṃ cāpi na svataḥ sarvadehinām || 30 ||
vaidikānāṃ tathā'nyeṣāmapi muktirhi sidhyati || 31 ||
