mahādevaṃ mahātmānaṃ bhaja kāruṇikottamam || 49 ||
mahādevaṃ samāśritya vāñchitaṃ nā''pnuyādyadi ||
mahādevo mahādevaṃ kathamanyaṃ samāśrayet || 50 ||
nāmataśvārthataśvāpi mahādevo maheśvaraḥ ||
tadanye kevalaṃ devā mahādevā na te'nagha || 51 ||
nāsti tasya vinirmokṣaḥ saṃsārājjanmakoṭibhiḥ||52||
śivādanyaṃ parityajya śivaṃ sāmvaṃ sadā bhaja || 53 ||
evamuktvā hariḥ śrīmānkirīṭī garuḍadhvajaḥ ||
sarvavijñānasaṃpannastatraivāntarhito'bhavat || 54 ||
satyasaṃdho mahādhīmānmahāviṣṇoḥ prasādataḥ ||
parityajyākhilāndevānāśrito'bhavadīśvaram || 55 ||
sarvamuktaṃ samāsena yuṣmākaṃ munipuṅgavāḥ ||
mama vākye'tiviśvāsaṃ kurudhvaṃ yatnato dijāḥ || 58 ||
na kathitavyamaśiṣṭajanasya tu || 59 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi śivabhakti samāsataḥ ||
yayā muktirvimuktiśca munīndrāḥ sarvadehinām || 1 ||
ekā śaṃkarasāyujyaśravā sāratarā parā || 2 ||
anyā śaṃkarasārūpya śradvā'tīva śivapriyā ||
