pūjopakaraṇaśraddhā cāpi bhaktirudīryate || 10 ||
tathaivotsavasevā ca bhaktiruktā'tiśobhanā || 11 ||
annapānapradānaṃ ca śivabhaktirudīritā || 12 ||
mahādevakathādīnāṃ śravaṇecchā maharṣayaḥ ||
mahābhaktiriti proktā mahāmāheśvarairjanaiḥ || 13 ||
vikāraḥ svaranetrāderbhaktiruktā mahātmabhiḥ || 14 ||
udyānakaraṇaṃ śaṃbho: śivabhaktirudāhṛtā ||
vāpīkūpataḍāgādikaraṇaṃ ca manīṣibhiḥ || 15 ||
prākāragopurādīnāṃ śivasyāmitatejasaḥ ||
iṣṭakādyaiśva nirmāṇaṃ śivabhaktirudīritā || 16 ||
śivaśāsanayuktasya pūjā śraddhā puraḥsaram ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivabhaktiparāyaṇaiḥ || 17 ||
naimittikānāṃ karaṇamapi bhaktiḥ śivasya tu || 18 ||
abhyāsaḥ śivavidyāyāstasyā adhyāpanaṃ tathā ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivaṃdṛṣṭiparāyaṇaiḥ || 19 ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivaśāstraviśāradaiḥ || 20 ||
śivapustakanikṣepasthānanirmāṇamāstikāḥ ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivadṛṣṭiparāyaṇaiḥ || 21 ||
śivajñānaikaniṣṭhasya maṭhikādānameva ca ||
annapānādidānaṃ ca śivabhaktirudīritā || 22 ||
śivajñānaikaniṣṭhasya śuśrūṣā śradvayā saha ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivabhaktiparāyaṇaiḥ || 23 ||
jāpināṃ śivamantrasya śuśrūṣā ca mahātmanām ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivatattvavicintakaiḥ || 24 ||
śivayātrāparāṇāṃ tu śuśrūṣā ca tathaiva ca ||
śivayātrā ca vidvadbhiḥ śivabhaktiḥ prakīrtitā || 25 ||
śivayātrāparāṇāṃ tu bādhakānāṃ tu vādhanam ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivayātrāparāyaṇaiḥ || 26 ||
śivāparādhaniṣṭhānāṃ chedanaṃ parayā mudā ||
śivabhaktiriti proktā śivārādhanatatparaiḥ || 27 ||
śivajñānaikaniṣṭhānāṃ śivajñānasya suvratāḥ ||
dūpakasya śiraśchedaḥ śivabhaktiḥ prakīrtitā || 28 ||
bhasmasādhananiṣṭhānāṃ dūpakasya munīśvarāḥ ||
chedanaṃ śirasaḥ sākṣācchivabhaktirudīritā || 29 ||
viṣṇvādīnāṃ tu devānāṃ dūpakasya durātmanaḥ ||
vādhanaṃ śivabhaktistu proktā vedāntavedibhiḥ || 30 ||
viṣṇvādidevatābhaktasyeva dūpaṇakāriṇaḥ ||
vādhamaṃ ca mahāprājñaiḥ śivabhaktiḥ prakīrtitā || 31 ||
āturāṇāṃ nṛṇāṃ rakṣā rakṣakāṇāṃ ca rakṣaṇam ||
bhītasyābhayadānaṃ ca śivabhaktiḥ prakīrtitā || 33 ||
sarvabhūteṣu kāruṇyaṃ priyabhāṣaṇameva ca ||
sarvabhūtahite śraddhā sākṣādbhaktiḥ śivasya tu || 34 ||
sarvabhūteṣu doṣasyādarśanaṃ guṇadarśanam ||
sarvabhūteṣu maitrī ca śivabhaktirudīritā || 35 ||
mahādeve'tiviśvāso viśvāsaḥ śivavedane ||
vedānteṣu ca viśvāsaḥ śivabhaktirudīritā || 36 ||
guruktārtheṣu viśvāso guruśuśrūṣaṇaṃ tathā ||
sā'pi bhaktiriti proktā vedavedāntavedibhiḥ || 37 ||
bhaktireva paramuktikāriṇī || 38 ||
pratītāṅgītikādasmādbhūtāni munipuṅgavāḥ ||
utkṛṣṭāni tathā tebhyo jīvātmā cetanaḥ prabhuḥ || 3 ||
āsāṃ samaṣṭibhūtastu śreṣṭhaḥ sarvātmanā budhāḥ || 5 ||
tato viśiṣṭāḥ sakalā brahmaṇastu vibhūtayaḥ ||
tāścānyonyaṃ viśiṣṭāḥ syuryathā jīvā munīśvarāḥ ||6||
tāsāṃ brahmā'dhikastasmāddiṣṇurmukhyaḥ prakīrtitaḥ ||
so'pi svavyaṣṭibhūtebhyo variṣṭhaḥ parikīrtitaḥ || 7 ||
brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśva paratattvavibhūtayaḥ || 8 ||
eri ayāṇāmadhikaḥ sarvakāraṇamīśvaraḥ ||
- rudrānandaśataṃ sarvakāraṇasya śivasya tu || 12 ||
satya cinmātrarūpasya bhūmā''nanda udāhṛtaḥ || 13 ||
evaṃ krameṇa sarveṣāṃ jñānādhikyamapīṣyate ||
skandhaśākhādibhedena yathā vṛkṣo vyavasthitaḥ || 14 ||
utkarṣaśvāpakarṣaśca skandhaśākhādivastuṣu || 15 ||
utkarṣaśvāpakarṣaśca tathā rudrādipu sthitaḥ || 16 ||
viśvādhiko rudro maharṣiriti śruteśca śivasyaiva viśvādhikatvam || 17 ||
vyāvahārikadṛṣṭayā'yaṃ vibhāgaḥ parikīrtitaḥ || 18 ||
pramāṇadṛṣṭyā vastvekameva nityaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||
anādṛtya mahāmohātpramāṇaṃ bhuvi mānavāḥ || 19 ||
mahāpāpavatāṃ nṛṇāṃ rudrādhikyaṃ na bhāsate || 20 ||
rudrādhikyaṃ svato bhāti pramāṇairapi tarkataḥ || 21 ||
sopānakramato devā nṛṇāṃ saṃsāramocakāḥ ||
rudraḥ saṃsāramagnānāṃ sākṣātsaṃsāramocakaḥ || 22 ||
śiva ekaḥ sadā dhyeyaḥ sākṣātsaṃsāramocakaḥ || 23 ||
vṛkṣasya mūlasekena śākhāḥ puṣyanti vai yathā ||
śivadhyānena devāśva tathā tṛptā bhavanti hi || 24 ||
na ca nāmāni rūpāṇi śivasya paramātmanaḥ ||
tathā'pi māyayā tasya nāmarūpe prakalpite || 28 ||
evamādīni nāmāni viśiṣṭāni parasya tu || 29 ||
viṣṇunārāyaṇādīni nāmāni parameśvare ||
kathaṃcidyoga tyā tu vartante na tu mukhyayā || 30 ||
arūpasya śivasyāpi mūrtiyā pāsakaiḥ ||
umārdhavigrahā śuklā trinetrā candraśekharā || 31 ||
nīlagrīvā parānandapramodā tāṇḍavapriyā ||
brahmaviṣṇumahādevairupāsyā guṇamūrtibhiḥ || 32 ||
tathā'pyeṣā parā mūrtirityeṣā śāśvatī śrutiḥ || 33 ||
viṣṇvādīnāṃ tu sarveṣāṃ mūrtayo vyavadhānataḥ ||
na tulyāḥ paratattvasya mṛsa vedāntapāragāḥ || 35 ||
yaprasidhyaiva vartanta iti śīghrapratītijanakatvānmukhyānītyabhiprāyaḥ || 35 ||
viṣṇvādīnāṃ ca devānāṃ tāni nāmāni suvratāḥ ||
tattvānvayena nāmāni bhavanti brahmavittamāḥ || 37 ||
annādibhojanānnṛṇāṃ yathā kṣuddinivartate ||
tathā mūrtiprasādena tattattvaṃ ca prakāśate || 40 ||
tasya mūrtiprasādena vinā naiva prakāśate || 41 ||
ato mūrti mahābhaktyā bhajadhvaṃ munipuṅgavāḥ || 42 ||
