sidhyet 1 atha tṛtīyaṃ jñānāntaraṃ tasyāpi prakāśāvaśyaṃbhāvājjñānāntaraṃ
śūnyasiddhirapi śreṣṭhāḥ śūnyenaiva na sidhyati ||
