ataḥ sākṣī śivaḥ sāmvaḥ svaprakāśakalakṣaṇaḥ ||
tena sarvamidaṃ gamyaṃ gamyate'sau na gamyate || 7 ||
na vibhātīva vibhāti māyayā ||
svata eva śrutikovidāḥ śivaḥ
svakaliṅgena nigamyate sphuṭam ||12||
dvahuprakāraṃ vyavahāradṛṣṭyā ||
svayaṃprabhasyāsya na cāsti liṅgam || 13 ||
evaṃ svaprakāśasyāpi śivasya māyāvaśādajñāyamānasya gamakāni liṅgāni
bruvanti cānye paramasya liṅgam || 14 ||
smṛtijāmitihāsajāmimāṃ
paravidyāmapi liṅgamīśituḥ ||
atiśudvāmapi tāṃ purāṇajāṃ
pravadanti śrutivittamottamāḥ || 15 ||
śivasya liṅgaṃ kathayanti māyāṃ
śivasya dṛśyāṃ śivavastuniṣṭhām ||
vahaṃkṛtiṃ cāpi manaśva buddhim || 16 ||
tsamūhamanye parameśvarasya || 17 ||
ālayo nāma cāssdhāraḥ sarvādhāraḥ śivaḥ khalu ||
sadāsatyasvabhāvatvātsatya eva śivaḥ khalu || 22 ||
hi vastuni śuktikāśakalādau māyāmayarajatādikaṃ parikalpitaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ śivaśva
asatyatvasya dṛṣṭatvādacihnasya vastunaḥ || 23 ||
śuktikārajataṃ viprāḥ satya eva tataḥ śivaḥ ||
ataḥ kalpitarūpāṇāmādhāro bhagavāśivaḥ || 25 ||
paraśivaspāsskāśasvādhiṣṭhānānvaraṃ nopapadyata
vyāvartayati cā''dhāraṃ śivasya paramātmanaḥ || 27 ||
vedāntavākyaṃ mānānāmatimānamiti sthitiḥ ||28||
āśritpāyaṃ prapañcaḥ syādalīko'pi pramāṇavān ||
svayameva sadā liṅgaṃ na liṅgaṃ tasya vidyate || 29 ||
saṃsārārṇavamagnānāmajñānāndhīkṛtātmanām ||
cittapākāṃnuguṇyena bhāvanārthe dvijarṣabhāḥ || 30 ||
ādhāro mantrasaṃskārātkalpitaḥ satyavabudhāḥ ||31||
śuktikārajatādīnāmasatyānāṃ dvijarṣabhāḥ ||
layo dṛṣṭo na satyasya śuktikāśakalasya ca || 34 ||
līyate hi śivādanyadaśeṣamaśivaṃ śive ||
ato liṅgaṃ dvijaśreṣṭhā avināśī heraḥ svayam || 35 ||
tṛtīyasthaṃ sadaivordhvamukhaṃ saṃsāranāśakam || 40 ||
gurūpadeśato jñeyaṃ dvitīyaṃ liṅgamīritam || 41 ||
visargādhiṣṭhitaṃ viśvaṃ viśvavijñānasādhakam || 43 ||
gurūpadeśato jñeyaṃ tṛtīyaṃ liṅgamīritam || 44 ||
eteṣu liṅgeṣu śivaḥ purāṇaḥ
lavābhilāpairabhipūjanīyaḥ || 45 ||
kuryādāśu brahmavidbrahmaniṣṭhāḥ
satyaṃ proktaṃ sarvalokapriyāya || 46 ||
puppatoyaphalapramukhāḥ kṛśāḥ || 47 ||
saṃsārasaṃjñasya munīndramukhyā
nālaṃ sadā mūlavimūlanāya || 48 ||
jñānameva śivārcanamiṣyate
bodha eva paramaṃ padamāstikāḥ || 49 ||
vyāsa āmaraṇāntikamāstikāḥ
pūjayadhvamasatyanivṛttaye || 50 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi śivasthānaṃ samāsataḥ ||
yatra saṃcintya deveśaṃ kaivalyaṃ labhate naraḥ || 1 ||
purā nārāyaṇaḥ śrīmānkirīṭī garuḍadhvajaḥ ||
