stotramārabhate viṣṇuḥ sarvabhūtahitāvaham || 6 ||
akārāya namaḥ sākṣādanantānandamūrtaye ||
ātmabhūtāya sarveṣāmatiśudvāya śūline || 7 ||
ākārāyātiśudvāya sākṣiṇe sarvavastunaḥ ||
ambikāpataye tubhyamasaṅgāya namo namaḥ || 8 ||
īkārāya variṣṭhāya vāñchitārthapradāya ca ||
vañcakānāmalabhyāya vasudāya namo namaḥ || 10 ||
ukārāyograjantūnāmugrarūpāya śūline |
uttamānāṃ tu jantūnāmupāsyāya namo namaḥ || 11 ||
ūkārāyopavītāya rjitāyottamātmane ||
uttamajñānagamyāya namaste paramātmane || 12 ||
upavītāpa bhogamokṣārthibhiḥ sakalalokairupagatāpa || 12 ||
ṛkārāyā''dibhūtāya rāmapūrvārcitāya ca ||
ṛcāmarthasvarūpāya namaḥ satyaparātmane || 13 ||
iti viśeṣya svarūpopanyāseneti draṣṭavyam || 13 ||
ṛkārāya nisargāya nityatṛptāya śaṃbhave ||
rasādibhūtarūpāya namaḥ śuddhacidātmane || 14 ||
ḷkārāya lasadgaṇḍamaṇḍitābharaṇāya ca ||
liṅgaliṅgayādihīnāya liṅgarūpāya te namaḥ || 15 ||
ekārāya namaḥ śaśvaditāsākṣiṇe tathā ||
ahaṃtāsākṣiṇe sākṣātpratyagaddyavastu || 17 ||
'bhinnā'haṃkārastadrūpa mānatvādvastutvam || 17 ||
aikārāyāmalajñānaprabhāvapariśīlinām ||
ātmarūpatayā nityaṃ pratītāya namo namaḥ || 18 ||
okārāya viriñcāya viṣṇave rudramūrtaye ||
vācyavācakahīnāya svayaṃbhānāya vai namaḥ || 19 ||
maukārāya maheśāya mahāmantrārtharūpiṇe |
mahādevāya mātrādimapañcāya namo namaḥ || 20 ||
vindurūpāya vījāya vījādhiṣṭhānarūpiṇe |
vījanāśakarajñānasvarūpāya namo namaḥ || 21 ||
visarjanīyaniṣṭhānāṃ viśeṣārthāya vai namaḥ || 22 ||
kakārāya kapūrvādidevatāpūjitāya ca ||
karaṇagrāma saṃhartre kālātītāya vai namaḥ || 23 ||
khamūrtaya khalaprajñāgocarāya namo namaḥ || 24 ||
gakārāya gaṇeśāya gaṇavṛndārcitāya ca ||
gaṅgādharāya gṛhyāya guṇātītāya te namaḥ || 25 ||
chakārāya cchalālasyacchādanādiviśeṣataḥ ||
chādanacchandanacchanna vibhāgāya namo namaḥ || 29 ||
jhakārāya jhamantrārthasvarūpāyāmṛtātmane ||
jhamadhyacandrabimbāya namaḥ sāmbāya śaṃbhave || 31 ||
ṭakārāya ṭāṭī pūrvakaistu mahāravaiḥ ||
arcitāya suraśreṣṭhairasuraiśca namo namaḥ || 33 ||
ṭhakārāya mantrārthasvarūpāya ṭhamantrataḥ ||
ṭhaṭhādigaṇapūjyāya ṭhamadhyāya namo namaḥ || 34 ||
ḍakārāya ḍaḍāḍī ḍūḍeḍoḍeśva mahāravaiḥ ||
ḍāmarairabhipūjyāya namo nṛtyapriyāya ca || 35 ||
hetava iti taiḥ pūjpāpetyuktam || 35 ||
ḍhakārāya umantrārthaparijñānavatāṃ nṛṇām ||
dasaṃjñitamahānandamadāya satataṃ namaḥ || 36 ||
ṇakārāya gaṇāṇīpūṇeṇeoṇākhaiḥ sadā ||
ṇākinīgaṇapūjyāya ṇasaṃjñāya namo namaḥ || 37 ||
dakārāya dayārūpamahāśaktimayāya ca ||
deśajātivihīnāya divārātrāya vai namaḥ || 40 ||
dhakārāya dharaṇyādimahābhūtasvarūpiṇe ||
dharādhara hṛdisthāya dhamadhyāya namo namaḥ || 41 ||
namaḥ śivāya namyāya nānārūpāya śūline || 42 ||
parāparavihīnāya pāvanāya namo namaḥ || 43 ||
bakārāya bakārākhyamahābījaikajāpinām ||
bandhanāgāranāśaikahetave vedhase namaḥ || 45 ||
makārāya mahāmāyāpāśanāśaikahetave ||
mamakāravihīnānāṃ mahānandāya vai namaḥ || 47 ||
yakārāya yathārthāya yathārthajñānināṃ nṛṇām ||
yathārthapratyagatabrahmaṇe satataṃ namaḥ || 48 ||
vakārāya variṣṭhāya vāsudevādihetave ||
vāñchāvāguravicchittihetubhūtāya vai namaḥ || 51 ||
śakārāya śaraṇyāya śaṃbhave śaraṇārthinām ||
śaraṇāya śaraccandradhavalāya namo namaḥ || 52 ||
ṣakārāya paḍādhāraṣaṭcakrādisvarūpiṇe |
ṣaḍakṣaraniṣaṇṇāya namaḥ ṣaṇmukhahetave || 53 ||
sākṣiṇe'sākṣirūpāṇāṃ namaḥ sādhūpakāriṇe || 954 ||
hakārāyāhamarthāya sadā'haṃkārasākṣiṇe ||
