pratipādyatayā tadātmane || 55 ||
lolācañcalasaṃsāranāśanāya namo namaḥ || 56 ||
saṃsārastannāśanāya || 56 ||
kṣakārāya kṣamantrārthasvarūpāya kṣamāvatām ||
kṣemadāya mama kṣemasvarūpāya namo namaḥ || 57 ||
mātṛkāvapuṣe mātṛmānameyādisākṣiṇe ||
mātṛkāmantralabhyāya mahase ca namo namaḥ || 58 ||
mātṛkādhārabhūtāya mātṛkāmūlarūpiṇe |
mahāmantraikavācyāya mahase brahmaṇe namaḥ || 59 ||
aṣṭadhā cāṣṭavargaistu vibhaktāyāmātmane ||
aśeṣaśabdabhūtāya tattadarthāya vai namaḥ || 61 ||
śabdānvayavihīnāya śabdalabhyāya sākṣiṇe ||
sarvopādhivihīnāya svayaṃbhānāya vai namaḥ || 62 ||
pratyakṣādipramāṇānāmagamyāyāparokṣataḥ ||
pratītāya svayaṃ sarvasākṣiṇe mahase namaḥ || 63 ||
evaṃ nārāyaṇenaiva śaṃkaro'bhiṣṭataḥ punaḥ ||
prāha gambhīrayā vācā kimarthaṃ taptavāṃstapaḥ || 66 ||
ityākarṇya mahāviṣṇuḥ praṇamya parameśvaram ||
tava sthānāni me deva brūhi sākṣātkṛpākara || 67 ||
ityukto viṣṇunā śaṃbhuḥ sarvajñaḥ karuṇākaraḥ ||
prāha sarveśvareśānaḥ sthānāni svasya viṣṇave || 68 ||
svargāpavargasiddhyarthamupāsyāni manīṣibhiḥ || 70 ||
gaṇḍopṭhadantamūrdhā ca sthānānyāsye mamānava || 73 ||
pṛṣṭhaśca nābhideśaśca hṛddeśaśca janārdana ||
dhātavaḥ sapta me sākṣātsthānāni puruṣottama || 75 ||
mūlādhāramadhiṣṭhānaṃ parakākhyamanāhatam ||
viśudvākhyaṃ ca matsthānaṃ viddhi paṅkajalocana ||76||
mahājñāsidvisaṃjñaṃ ca viṣṇo vārāṇasī purī ||
praṇavāṃśatrayaṃ vindunādaśaktisamāhvayam || 77 ||
vījasthānaṃ ca meḍhraṃ ca romāṇi vividhāni ca ||
mama sthānāni kalyāṇa viddhi pajalocana || 78 ||
yathā'dhyātme mahāviṣṇo sthānāni subahūni me ||
tathā'vibhūte me viṣṇo sthānāni subahūni ca || 79 ||
kailāsaparvataḥ sākṣātsthānaṃ viṣṇo mamānagha ||
śrīmaddakṣiṇa kailāsaparvataśca tathaiva ca || 80 ||
vārāṇasī purī puṇyā vimuktiphaladā nṛṇām ||
maraṇādeva sarveṣāṃ tacca sthānaṃ mamānagha || 81 ||
śrīparvataṃ ca me sthānaṃ viddhi paṅkajalocana || 82 ||
śrīmadvācalaṃ puṇyaṃ tathā goparvataṃ hare ||
tathā śrīharatīrthaṃ ca viddhi sthānaṃ mamāvyayam || 83 ||
dantisthānaṃ ca me viṣṇo sthānaṃ viddhi mahattaram ||84||
madhyārjunaṃ ca me sthānaṃ viddhi paṅkajalocana || 85 ||
śrīmanmaṅgalavaṃśākhyaṃ kumbhakoṇasamāhvayam ||
tathā savyetarāva viddhi sthānaṃ mamānagha || 86 ||
gajāraṇyasamākhyaṃ me viddhi sthānaṃ vicakṣaṇa || 87 ||
vedāraṇyasamākhyaṃ ca tathā hālāsyasaṃjñitam ||
śrīmadrāmeśvarākhyaṃ ca sthānaṃ viddhi mamādbhutam || 88 ||
bhogamuktiphaladaṃ purātanam || 89 ||
