sarvastrībhirdhṛtaṃ bhasma tripuṇḍromūlanātmanā || 47 ||
munibhiśca dhṛtaṃ bhasma tripuṇḍroḍūlanātmanā || 48 ||
brāhmaṇaiḥ kṣatriyairvaiśyaiḥ śūdrepei ca saṃkaraiḥ ||
apabhraṃśairdhṛtaṃ bhasma tripuṇḍolanātmanā || 49 ||
udūlanaṃ tripuṇḍraṃ ca yaiḥ samācaritaṃ mudā ||
ta eva śiṣṭā vidvāṃso netare munipuṅgavāḥ || 50 ||
30 adhyāyaḥ
udūlanaṃ tripuṇḍraṃ ca śradvayā nā''caranti ye ||
teṣāṃ nāsti vinirmokṣaḥ saṃsārājjanmakoṭibhiḥ || 51 ||
teṣāṃ nāsti śivajñānaṃ kalpakoṭiśatairapi || 52 ||
teṣāṃ nāsti samācāro varṇāśramasamanvitaḥ || 53 ||
ubūlanaṃ tripuṇḍraṃ ca śraddhayā nā''caranti ye ||
te mahāpātakairyuktā iti śāstrasya nirṇayaḥ || 54 ||
uyūlanaṃ tripuṇḍaṃ ca śraddhayā nā''caranti ye ||
taiḥ samācaritaṃ sarva viparītaphalāya hi || 55 ||
mahāpātakayuktānāṃ jantūnāṃ pūrvajanmasu ||
tripuṇḍronūlanadveṣo jāyate sudṛḍhaṃ budhāḥ || 56 ||
tripuṇḍrolane śraddhā yeṣāṃ naivopajāyate ||
upapātakadoṣeṇa duṣṭāste nātra saṃśayaḥ || 57 ||
vāñchā na jāyate yeṣāṃ te mahāpāpasaṃyutāḥ || 58 ||
te mahāpātakairyuktā iti me niścitā matiḥ || 59 ||
guruṇā cāpi me viprāḥ kalpakoṭiśatairāpe || 60 ||
brahmaṇā viṣṇunā cāpi rudreṇāpi munīśvarāḥ ||
bhasmadhāraṇamāhātmyaṃ na śakyaṃ paribhāṣitum || 61 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi śivaprītikaraṃ mudā ||
śradvayā saha viprendrāḥ śṛṇutātīva śobhanam || 1 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 2 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 3 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 4 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 5 ||
śivaśaṃkararudrādiśabdābhyāsaśva sādaram ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraḥ sadā || 6 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikarī sadā || 7 ||
śrutismṛtipurāṇeṣu viśvāso yaḥ sa āstikāḥ ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraḥ sadā || 8 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 9 ||
vedavedāntavākyānāṃ tātparyasya nirūpaṇam ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 10 ||
tripuṇḍroḍūlanācāro jābāloktena vartmanā ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraḥ sadā || 11 ||
kaṇṭhe śirasi vā haste rudrākṣāṇāṃ ca dhāraṇam ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 12 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 13 ||
vārāṇasyādike sthāne yātrākaraṇamādarāva ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 14 ||
śāntidāntyādisaṃpattirmumukṣutvaṃ munīśvarāḥ ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 15 ||
nityānityārthavijñānaṃ vairāgyaṃ sudṛḍhaṃ tathā ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 16 ||
yajñadānatapaḥkarmaniṣṭhā cā''śramarakṣaṇam ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 17 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 18 ||
niṣiddhakarmaṇāṃ tyāgo durvṛttānāmupekṣaṇam ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 19 ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikaraṃ sadā || 20 ||
dvijānāmapi śuśrūṣā jñānināṃ ca viśeṣataḥ ||
devadevasya viprendrā mahāprītikarī sadā || 21 ||
śivajñānaikaniṣṭhasya guroḥ śuśrūṣaṇaṃ sadā ||
śivaprītikarāṇāṃ tu viśiṣṭaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ || 22 ||
purā kācitkulālastrī babhūvātīva sundarī ||
sā sahasratrayaṃ hatvā viprāṇāmarthavāñchyā || 23 ||
mahādhanavatī bhūtvā māyayā parimohitā ||
yatheṣṭaṃ bhūtale viprāśvacāra parigarvitā || 24 ||
kaśviddijñānasaṃpanno mahāyogī suniścalaḥ ||
śrīmaddakṣiṇa kailāsaṃ śivasthānottamottamam || 25 ||
sūtasaṃhitā 1
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sā svabhogārthaṃ praṇipatya tapasvinam || 26 ||
parigṛhyātisaṃtuṣṭā gṛhe svīye vicakṣaṇā ||
nāpya vastrādikaṃ dattvā bhojayitvā'numoditaḥ || 27 ||
samāśvāsya mahātmānaṃ priyaṃ bhuktavatī dvijāḥ || 28 ||
atīva prītimāpannastayā saha munīśvarāḥ || 29 ||
avartata ciraṃ kālamatīva prītisaṃyutaḥ || 30 ||
devadevo mahāprītastayā śuśrūṣayā dvijāḥ ||
tasyai paramakaivalyaṃ dadau vijñānapūrvakam || 31 ||
bahavo jñānaniṣṭasya śuśrūpāvalato dvijāḥ ||
śivaprītimavāpyā''śu vimuktā bhavabandhanāt || 32 ||
ata ukteṣu sarveṣu śuśrūṣā śivayoginaḥ ||
śivaprītikarī sākṣāditi vedārthasaṃgrahaḥ || 33 ||
ataḥ śivaprītikaraṃ vicārya dvijottamā vedavidāṃ variṣṭhāḥ ||
maduktamārgeṇa śivapriyeṇa sadāśivaprītikaraṃ kurudhvam ||34||
pañca sapta ca varṣāṇi na vavarṣa śatakratuḥ || 2 ||
anādṛṣṭayā dijā bhūmirdurbhikṣā'bhavadāstikāḥ ||
kṣutpīḍā ca mahātīvrā vijātā sarvadehinām || 3 ||
manuṣyāśvāsamācārā abhavannannavāñchayā ||
hatvā kecinmanuṣyāṃśca bhuktavanto vimohitāḥ|| 4 ||
turaṃgāṃśca gajānkeciduktavanto yathābalam || 5 ||
brāhmaṇāḥ kecidāloḍya viśiṣṭā munisattamāḥ ||
gautamasyāssśramaṃ puṇyaṃ yayuḥ sarve mahattaram || 6||
āśramastasya viprendrāḥ subhikṣastvabhavaddhṛśam || 7 ||
procuḥ kleśena saṃyuktā dvijāḥ kāruṇikaṃ prati || 8 ||
kevalaṃ kṛpayaivāsmānrakṣa rakṣa hite rata || 9 ||
iti vijñāpitaḥ śrīmānmahākāruṇikottamaḥ ||
gautamaḥ sarvaviprāṇāmabhayaṃ dattavānprabhuḥ || 10 ||
putrabhāryādiyuktānāṃ viprāṇāṃ gautamo muniḥ ||
dadau dhānyaṃ dhanaṃ vastraṃ tilaṃ tailaṃ ca gāmapi || 11 ||
anyāni yāni jantūnāmiṣṭāni sakalāni tu ||
tāni teṣāṃ muniḥ śrīmāndadau kāruṇikottamaḥ || 12 ||
ādhivyābhyastraśastrādipīḍāśca vividhā dvijāḥ ||
śrautasmārtasamācārā upadiṣṭā dvijanmanām ||
gautamena munīndreṇa munīndrāḥ karuṇāvalāt || 14 ||
tapasā kevalaṃ bhūmiḥ subhikṣā'bhavadāstikāḥ || 15 ||
vicārya kārya saṃbhūya svadeśagamanāya vai || 16 ||
kṛto mithyābhiśāpastu mahāmohavaśena tu || 17 ||
mahākrodhena saṃyuktaḥ śaśāpa brāhmaṇādhamān || 18 ||
mahādevasya bhaktau ca mahādevasya nāmni ca || 19 ||
mahādevasya ca sthāne mahādevasya kīrtiṣu || 20 ||
mahādevāya dāne ca mahādevāśrayeṣu ca ||
mahādevasya cotkarṣe tripuṇḍronūlanādiṣu || 21 ||
rudrālayadidṛkṣāyāṃ rudrayātrādikarmasu || 22 ||
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 23 ||
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 24 ||
śāntidāntyādivijñānasādhaneṣu dvijādhamāḥ ||
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 25 ||
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 26 ||
nānāvidheṣu dāneṣu yajñeṣu vividheṣu ca ||
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 27 ||
kṛcchracāndrāyaṇādau ca tathā māsopavāsake |
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 28 ||
bhavatānummukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 29 ||
bhavatānunmukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 30 ||
avatānamukhā yūyaṃ sarvadā brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 31 ||
sūtasaṃhitā 1,
śaṅkhacakragadāpadmadaṇḍapāśāṃkuśādibhiḥ ||
aṅkitāḥ śraddhayā yūyaṃ bhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 33 ||
aṅkitāḥ śraddhayā yūyaṃ bhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 34 ||
bhavata śraddhā sā lalāṭe brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 35 ||
pitṛmātṛsutabhātṛbhāryāvikrayiṇaḥ sadā ||
dharmavikrayiṇastaddadbhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 37 ||
matsyavikrayiṇastaddadbhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 38 ||
pāñcarātre ca kāpāle tathā kālāmukhe'pi ca ||
śākte ca dīkṣitā yūyaṃ bhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 39 ||
śāṃbhave dīkṣitā yūyaṃ bhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 40 ||
pāpaṇḍeṣu tathā'nyeṣu mārgeṣva śrautakeṣu ca ||
śradvayā dīkṣitā yūyaṃ bhavata brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 41 ||
yuṣmākaṃ vaṃśajātāca sarve strībhiḥ saha dvijāḥ ||
maduktārthaprakāreṇa bhavantu brāhmaṇādhamāḥ || 42 ||
tatsaṃvandhiṣu sarveṣu śrutismṛtyādikeṣu ca || 43 ||
yuṣmākaṃ vaṃśajātānāṃ yuṣmākaṃ ca tathaiva ca ||
śradvābhāvaḥ sadevāstu śāpastītraḥ kṛto mayā || 44 ||
evaṃ munīndreṇa kṛte ca śāṃpe
dvijādhamāśvāpi tadājñayaiva ||
svabhāvajo hyeṣa muneḥ prabhāvaḥ || 45 ||
tripuṇḍra mudūlanamāstikottamāḥ
viśeṣataḥ śāṃkaravedane rato
bhavedaśeṣaṃ kathitaṃ mayā'naghāḥ || 47 ||
śarvaḥ paśupatiḥ sākṣī haraḥ śrīkaṇṭha * adbhutaḥ ||
ugraḥ kapardī giriśo bhavaḥ sarvajña īśvaraḥ || 3 ||
antakāristrinetraśca dakṣayajñavināśanaḥ || 4 ||
dhūrjaṭirvāmadevaśva sthāṇuḥ sarvavināśakaḥ ||
sraṣṭā ca pālakaścaiva tatastatpuruṣaḥ prabhuḥ ||5||
vāmadevaḥ kapālī ca sadyojātaḥ samaḥ sukhī ||
aghoraśva sughoraśva praśāntaḥ pāpanāśakaḥ || 6 ||
bhavārirbhogadaḥ puṇyaḥ kāmadhvaṃsī kapiñjaraḥ ||
vyomakeśī viśālākṣo vahniretā varapradaḥ || 7 ||
bhīmo bhargaḥ pinākī ca nṛpāṅkaḥ kālakūṭadhṛk |
kṛttivāsāḥ kirātaśca bhikṣuko mūlakāraṇam || 8 ||
mṛḍo merudharo medhā mahāmāyī maheśvaraḥ ||
sarvādhiṣṭhānamādhāraḥ sarvādhikaraṇaḥ svarāṭ ||
setuḥ sīmā samudraśva viśiṣṭaśva vidhārakaḥ || 11 ||
janmādikāraṇaṃ hetuḥ śāstrayoniḥ sukhāsanaḥ ||
tatsamo vā'dhiko'saṅga ātmā cāmalasādhanam ||12||
purāṇaḥ puruṣaḥ pūrṇo'nantarūpaḥ purātanaḥ ||
satyaṃ jñānaṃ sukhaṃ sākṣādākāśaḥ prāṇa āstikāḥ || 13 ||
jyotiḥprakāśaḥ prathitaḥ svayaṃbhānaḥ svayaṃprabhuḥ ||
svaprakāśaḥ svatantraśca svasthaḥ svānubhavo'gamaḥ || 14 ||
attā cānaśanaḥ śaṅkuḥ paramātmā parātparaḥ ||
devadevaśva devaśva jagannātho nirañjanaḥ || 15 ||
vido vidādhirvedāntā devatā paradevatā || 16 ||
patiḥ pāśaharaḥ pāraḥ pāraśūnyaḥ prajāpatiḥ ||
dhātā dhārayitā dhṛṣṭo dhāma dhāmavivarjitaḥ || 17 ||
sabhyaḥ stutyaḥ samastātmā sāmbaḥ saṃsāravarjitaḥ ||18||
saṃsāravaidyaḥ satyārthaḥ sāraḥ saṃsārabheṣajam ||
saṃsāramocako mocyo mukto mūladhanaṃ muniḥ || 19 ||
maharṣiśva mahāgrāso mahātmā madhuraḥ suraḥ ||
surajyeṣṭho virūpākṣo viśvarūpo vināyakaḥ || 20 ||
ahamartho'prameyaśca tattvaṃ nirvāṇamuttamam || 21 ||
adṛśyo dṛśyanetā ca netraṃ dṛṣṭiśva darśanam ||
dṛṣṭiḥ pavamānaśva vaśī vaiśvānaro naraḥ || 23 ||
mūlācāryo mukundeśo mūlamāyatanaṃ mahān ||
daharo divya advairtamanākhyaṃ vastu vāstavam || 24 ||
hakārī huṃ phaḍagrasto hārdo hatpāvano'vadhiḥ || 25 ||
vadanti nārāyaṇaviṣṇupūrvam ||
munīśvarā nāsti vimuktireṣāṃ
vibhūtireva kramaśo vimuktiḥ || 27 ||
satyameva paṭhitaṃ mayaiva tu || 28 ||
nāmāni sarvāṇi ca kalpitāni
tathā'pi mukhyāstu śivādiśabdā
bhavanti saṃkalpanayā śivasya || 29 ||
nṛtyati sma parameśayā saha || 30 ||
devarudraśivaśaṃkarādiṣu ||
koṭapūrvajanireva tasya hi || 31 ||
sūtasaṃhitā !
bhavanti nāmāni parasya cā''jñayā || 32 ||
ato mahādevaśivādiśabdaṃ
vihāya nārāyaṇapūrvaśabdaṃ
japedaśeṣāśubhanāśanāya || 33 ||
kāmakrodhamahālobhapaiśunyādivivarjitaḥ || 2 ||
ācārya satyasaṃpannaṃ sākṣātkāruṇikottamam ||
abhigamya mahātmānaṃ praṇasya bhuvi daṇḍavat || 3 ||
uttamaṃ kāñcanaṃ dattvā yathāśakti dhanaṃ tu vā ||
bahuśo daṇḍavaḍūmau praṇamya śraddhayā saha || 5 ||
adhīhi bhagavo brahmetyevaṃ vijñāpayetsudhīḥ || 6 ||
so'pi kāruṇikaḥ śrīmānguruḥ sarvārthavittamaḥ ||
susame supradeśe tu nirjane nirbhaye śubhe || 7 ||
pūrṇakumbhaiśca saṃyukte dīpairdikṣu samanvite || 8 ||
apakkaistaṇḍulaiḥ śuddhaiḥ śuddhairvā śālitaṇḍulaiḥ || 9 ||
kṛtāñjalipuṭaṃ pūrṇaprakāśanikarātmake ||
śivānande samāsīnamevaṃ bhāvanayā yutam || 12 ||
granthicchedaṃ punaḥ kuryādgurutenaiva vartmanā ||14 ||
tatsūtraṃ dakṣiṇe bhāge pādāṅguṣṭhāntamānayet ||
mumukṣorviparītena nārīṇāṃ vāmabhāgake |
kṛte kāruṇikenaivamācāryeṇa dvijottamāḥ || 15 ||
svātmabhūtāṃ parāṃ śaktiṃ prerayatyeva suvratāḥ || 16 ||
prasannā sā mahādevī mahākāruṇikottamā ||
śiṣyasyā''tmani cidrūpe svayaṃ patati nirmalā || 17||
śaktipāte tu saṃjāte śiṣyasyā''tmani saṃsthitā ||
māyā dagdhā bhavetkiṃcinnātra saṃdehakāraṇam || 18 ||
sarvasādhanasaṃyuktaḥ sākṣādāstikyasaṃyutaḥ ||
mahādevasya bhaktaścecchiṣyaḥ sadgurubhaktimān || 19 ||
tadā śiṣyasya cidrūpe kalpitā moharūpiṇī ||
māyā dagdhā bhavekiṃcittadā patati vigrahaḥ || 21 ||
prasādaḥ śāṃkarastasya dvijāḥ saṃjāta eva hi || 22 ||
yasya prasādaḥ saṃjāto dehapātāvasānakaḥ ||
kṛtārtha eva viprendrā na sa bhūyo'bhijāyate || 23 ||
dehatyavidyāmakhilāṃ tamaḥ sūryodayo yathā || 24 ||
ācāryācchrutavedāntaḥ kramānmucyeta bandhanāt || 25 ||
śaktipātena saṃyuktā vidyā vedāntavākyajā ||
yadā yasya tadā tasya vimuktirnātra saṃśayaḥ || 26 ||
śaktipātaprakārasya rahasyāṃśaśca kaścana ||
mayā noko rahasyatvādājñābhaṅgabhayādapi || 27 ||
dine dine guroḥ pūjāṃ kuryādarthādibhirnaraḥ || 28 ||
śaṃkareṇa purā kathitaṃ guroḥ śaṃkaraḥ khalu sarvahite rataḥ || 29 ||
athātaḥ saṃpravakṣyāmi saṃpradāya paraṃparām ||
yajjñānena dvijaśreṣṭho gururbhavati suvratāḥ || 1 ||
yaḥ śivaḥ sarvabhūtānāmīśvaraḥ svata eva tu ||
īśānaḥ sarvavidyānāṃ sa evā''digururbudhāḥ || 2 ||
tasya śiṣyo mahāviṣṇuḥ sarvajñānamahodadhiḥ ||
tasmādāttaparijñāno brahmā sarvajagatprabhuḥ || 3 ||
sanatkumārātsarvajñātkṛṣṇadvaipāyano muniḥ || 4 ||
avāptākhilavijñānastasmādeva śrutaṃ mayā ||
matto labdhaparijñānā yūyaṃ satyaparāyaṇāḥ || 5 ||
evaṃ buddhvā muniśreṣṭhāḥ saṃpradāyaparaṃparām ||
tattannāmnā namaskṛtya śraddhayā deśikānimāna || 6 ||
pūrvoktenaiva mārgeṇa kuryādajñānanāśanam ||
jācāryācchrutavedāntaḥ satyavāggurubhaktimān || 7 ||
svaguruṃ ca namaskṛtya śradvayā ca gurorgurum || 12 ||
vighneśaṃ ṣaṇmukhaṃ cāpi śivāṃ vidyāsvarūpiṇīm ||
anyāṃśca sakalāndevānbrahmaviṣṇupurogamān || 13 ||
punaḥ śiṣyasya medhāvī cittapākaṃ parīkṣya ca ||
avidyāpāśavicchedaṃ kuryātprājñastu deśikaḥ || 14 ||
viditvā śiṣyacittasya vipākaṃ punarāstikāḥ ||
dadyātpākānurūpeṇa vidyāmetāṃ maheśvarīm || 15 ||
mūrkhaśiṣyopadeśena vidyāgarveṇa suvratāḥ ||
gurudroheṇa sarvajño'pyandhakūpe patatyadhaḥ ||16||
tasmātsaṃvatsaraṃ śiṣyaṃ parīkṣyākṛtrimaṃ punaḥ ||
pradadyādvaidikīṃ vidyāṃ gururvidyābhivṛddhaye || 17 ||
vidyāsaṃtativijñānaṃ śiṣyacittaparīkṣaṇam ||
avaśyaṃbhāvi viprendrā deśikasyeśvarājñayā || 18 ||
saṃpradāyavihīnā yā vidyā vedāntapāragāḥ ||
sā'vidyā naiva vidyā syāditi tattvavidāṃ sthitiḥ||19||
pāraṃparyāvabodhena vidyā sā vīryavattarā || 20 ||
11 30 11
pāraṃparyaparijñānādeva pāśanikṛntanam ||
tasmātprājñaḥ svavidyāyāḥ saṃtatijñānavānbhavet ||21||
pāraṃparyaparijñānaṃ tathā jñānopakārakam || 22 ||
vidyāsaṃtatayo viprā bahurūpāḥ śrutau śrutāḥ ||
tattatsaṃtativijñānaṃ vidyāsiddhestu kāraṇam || 23 ||
yasya deśikaparaṃparā dhṛtā ||
śuddhavaṃśaparavedanena tu || 25 ||
saṃtānavijñānavihīnadeśikaḥ
saṃtānavijñānavataḥ sadāśivaḥ
svakaṃ vapustasya dadāti citsukham || 26 ||
na deśikatvaṃ na sukhitvamāstikāḥ ||27||
bhraṣṭaśca satyaṃ paribhāṣitaṃ mayā || 28 ||
sphuraṇasukhamanantaṃ saṃtatijñānahīnāḥ ||29||
atha patriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ 1
āmnāyāntaikasaṃsiddhaṃ sukaraṃ sarvadehinām || 1 ||
