muktyupāyamayatnena mayā notamitaḥ purā || 1 ||
svaguruṃ vedavedāntaviśāradamanuttamam || 2 ||
tapasā dīptasarvāṅgaṃ parāśarasutaṃ prabhum ||
praṇamya parayā prītyā daṇḍavatpṛthivītale || 3 ||
apṛcchalokarakṣārthamatigṛhyamanuttamam || 4 ||
vada kāruṇyato nātha mama māyāviṣāpaham || 5 ||
sādhu sādhu muniśreṣṭha tvayā pṛṣṭaṃ jagadvitam ||
purā purāṇaṃ brahmāṇamidaṃ pṛṣṭaṃ mayā'pi ca || 6 ||
brahmaṇā ca mahāviṣṇuḥ pṛṣṭastenāpi śaṃkaraḥ ||
sa punaḥ śaṃkaraḥ śrīmānambikāpatiruttamaḥ || 7 ||
viṣṇave lokarakṣārthaṃ babhāṣe karuṇānidhiḥ || 8 ||
sthāne pṛṣṭaṃ tvayā viṣṇo jagataḥ pālane rataḥ ||
vadāmi saṃgraheṇāhaṃ muktyupāyamayatnataḥ || 9 ||
sarvadā paramaprītyā yatra nṛtyaṃ karomyaham || 10 ||
dṛṣṭvā pañcākṣaraṃ mantraṃ satāraṃ sarvasiddhidam || 11 ||
tasya siddhā parā muktirvinā vijñānamuttamam || 12 ||
śrīmaddakṣiṇakailāse tathā vṛddhācalābhidhe ||
tathā goparvate śuddhe tathā valmīkasaṃjñite || 13 ||
somanāthe tu gokarṇe tathā bhīmeśvarābhidhe || 14 ||
vedāraṇye viśiṣṭe tu śvetāraṇye tu śobhane ||
hastikānanasaṃjñe ca tathā japyeśvarābhidhe || 15 ||
vārāṇasyāṃ tu kedāre tathā rāmeśvarābhidhe || 16 ||
