tasaṃhitā |
purā kaśvinmahāpāpī dvijaḥ puṇyavivarjitaḥ ||
mahāmohāvṛtaḥ sākṣānmātaraṃ tu pativratām || 18 ||
darśayati-— purā kaścidityādinā || 18 ||
nirghṛṇo nirbhayo nityaṃ cacāra vasudhātale || 19 ||
musalodyatapāṇistu vibhāti brahmarākṣasaḥ || 20 ||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā bhītisaṃyuktaḥ pūrvapuṇyabalena tu ||
hālāsyākhyaṃ mahāsthānamagamatpuruṣottama || 21 ||
adṛṣṭastatkṣaṇādeva tenaiva brahmarākṣasaḥ ||
so'pi vismayamāpanno vicārya kamalekṣaṇa || 22 ||
asmindeśe na dṛṣṭastu mayā sa brahmarākṣasaḥ || 23 ||
kāryamityabhisaṃdhiṃ ca hare kṛtvā suniścalaḥ || 24 ||
samastāni ca pāpāni vinaṣṭāni janārdana || 25 ||
śrutvā dṛṣṭvā tu māṃ nityaṃ hālāsyākhye'tiśobhane || 26 ||
ayatnena vimukto'bhūtsaṃsārajaladhestu saḥ || 27 ||
ato viśiṣṭe matsthāne cātraivānyatra vā naraḥ ||
dṛṣṭvā māmādareṇaiva japenmantraṃ ṣaḍakṣaram ||
ito'nyatsakalaṃ viṣṇo narāṇāṃ pāpakarmaṇām ||
aśakyaṃ kartumatyarthaṃ tasmāduktaṃ samācaret || 31 ||
purā satyavatīsūnuḥ sarvavijñānasāgaraḥ ||
sarvavedodadheḥ pāro gururme karuṇānidhiḥ || 2 ||
dhyāyamāno mahābhaktyā tatāpa paramaṃ tapaḥ || 3 ||
paḍakṣareṇa mantreṇa tuṣṭāvaṃ ca maheśvaram || 4 ||
brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśva īśvaraśva sadāśivaḥ ||
virāḍādyāśva devāśca yanmātraṃ taṃ numaḥ śivam || 7 ||
mahāsattvāśva ye jīvā madhyasattvācaṃ cetanāḥ ||
vihīnāścaiva yanmātraṃ taṃ namāmi mahaujasam || 8 ||
yaṃ vinā na jagattasmai sadā sākṣātsate namaḥ || 9 ||
ātmeti manvate vande tamindriyavilakṣaṇam || 19 ||
vande taṃ prāṇavettāraṃ prāṇaṃ prāṇasya sarvadā || 20 ||
ātmeti manvate bhaktyā vande taṃ manasaḥ param || 21 ||
taṃ vande buddhivodvāraṃ bodharūpamavikriyam || 22 ||
